Dialogue: 0,0:32:02.49,0:32:04.99,Default,,0,0,0,,by calibrating levels of truth
Dialogue: 0,0:32:04.99,0:32:07.79,Default,,0,0,0,,and following those things
Dialogue: 0,0:32:07.79,0:32:09.25,Default,,0,0,0,,which calibrate the highest.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:09.88,0:32:11.77,Default,,0,0,0,,In as much as we're born without that
Dialogue: 0,0:32:11.77,0:32:13.24,Default,,0,0,0,,capacity for discernment,
Dialogue: 0,0:32:14.00,0:32:15.51,Default,,0,0,0,,we have now
Dialogue: 0,0:32:15.51,0:32:17.57,Default,,0,0,0,,a methodology. We don't know altitude
Dialogue: 0,0:32:17.57,0:32:19.50,Default,,0,0,0,,by looking at a mountain either.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:20.14,0:32:21.50,Default,,0,0,0,,But we now have altimeters.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:21.81,0:32:23.83,Default,,0,0,0,,So, the advancement of human consciousness
Dialogue: 0,0:32:23.83,0:32:25.54,Default,,0,0,0,,has shown us
Dialogue: 0,0:32:25.54,0:32:26.95,Default,,0,0,0,,a different way.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:27.26,0:32:29.63,Default,,0,0,0,,A better way. One that's
Dialogue: 0,0:32:29.63,0:32:31.71,Default,,0,0,0,,impersonal. And I want to
Dialogue: 0,0:32:31.71,0:32:33.30,Default,,0,0,0,,emphasize again, it's impersonal.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:33.30,0:32:35.49,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't have any personal feeling about any of the calibrations
Dialogue: 0,0:32:35.49,0:32:37.08,Default,,0,0,0,,we do at all. I don't have any personal
Dialogue: 0,0:32:37.08,0:32:39.13,Default,,0,0,0,,calibration about it at all, correctly.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:39.89,0:32:41.39,Default,,0,0,0,,It's just whatever it is
Dialogue: 0,0:32:41.39,0:32:43.28,Default,,0,0,0,,is whatever it is. You know, like an altimeter,
Dialogue: 0,0:32:43.45,0:32:45.17,Default,,0,0,0,,you go up to the mountain and you read the dial.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:45.89,0:32:47.50,Default,,0,0,0,,So, with consciousness calibration
Dialogue: 0,0:32:47.50,0:32:48.84,Default,,0,0,0,,we just read the dial.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:49.32,0:32:51.34,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't personally have any investment in
Dialogue: 0,0:32:51.34,0:32:53.49,Default,,0,0,0,,what the answer is one way or the other.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:54.26,0:32:55.79,Default,,0,0,0,,In fact, if it comes out
Dialogue: 0,0:32:55.79,0:32:57.53,Default,,0,0,0,,different than what one expects,
Dialogue: 0,0:32:58.24,0:32:59.35,Default,,0,0,0,,that leads one to
Dialogue: 0,0:32:59.35,0:33:00.48,Default,,0,0,0,,important discoveries.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:00.48,0:33:01.03,Default,,0,0,0,,You know?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:01.83,0:33:04.77,Default,,0,0,0,,If there's a
Dialogue: 0,0:33:04.77,0:33:06.64,Default,,0,0,0,,differential between your expectation
Dialogue: 0,0:33:06.64,0:33:08.40,Default,,0,0,0,,and the result that you get, you know,
Dialogue: 0,0:33:08.96,0:33:10.50,Default,,0,0,0,,then that leads you to further
Dialogue: 0,0:33:10.50,0:33:12.40,Default,,0,0,0,,inquiry. And with further inquiry, then
Dialogue: 0,0:33:12.40,0:33:14.42,Default,,0,0,0,,you do discover the truth behind it.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:15.44,0:33:16.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Now, the question
Dialogue: 0,0:33:16.92,0:33:18.92,Default,,0,0,0,,was how do you differentiate between
Dialogue: 0,0:33:18.92,0:33:20.96,Default,,0,0,0,,divinity, reality, and truth?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:21.11,0:33:21.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Is that what it is?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:22.72,0:33:29.01,Default,,0,0,0,,We said that reality is that which
Dialogue: 0,0:33:29.01,0:33:30.03,Default,,0,0,0,,is confirmable.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:30.98,0:33:33.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Confirmable. So, then you have
Dialogue: 0,0:33:33.24,0:33:35.16,Default,,0,0,0,,truth which has to do with
Dialogue: 0,0:33:35.16,0:33:35.68,Default,,0,0,0,,essence.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:36.38,0:33:38.38,Default,,0,0,0,,And reality has to do with
Dialogue: 0,0:33:38.38,0:33:40.79,Default,,0,0,0,,content.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:40.79,0:33:43.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Reality is confirmable.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:43.59,0:33:45.59,Default,,0,0,0,,What is confirmable?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:45.59,0:33:47.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Therefore, it's linear.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:47.78,0:33:49.78,Default,,0,0,0,,It's here,
Dialogue: 0,0:33:49.78,0:33:51.78,Default,,0,0,0,,at this time, and it weighs this much,
Dialogue: 0,0:33:51.78,0:33:53.78,Default,,0,0,0,,and it measures this much, and it's
Dialogue: 0,0:33:53.78,0:33:56.03,Default,,0,0,0,,located right here.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:56.03,0:33:58.03,Default,,0,0,0,,So, that's all linear, confirmable.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:58.03,0:34:00.03,Default,,0,0,0,,And that's content
Dialogue: 0,0:34:00.03,0:34:02.20,Default,,0,0,0,,of consciousness.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:02.20,0:34:04.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Truth is of a different level. Truth has to
Dialogue: 0,0:34:04.20,0:34:06.40,Default,,0,0,0,,do with abstraction.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:06.40,0:34:08.40,Default,,0,0,0,,And truth is what escapes
Dialogue: 0,0:34:08.40,0:34:10.61,Default,,0,0,0,,people who are,
Dialogue: 0,0:34:10.61,0:34:12.61,Default,,0,0,0,,what do you say,
Dialogue: 0,0:34:12.61,0:34:14.61,Default,,0,0,0,,pedestrian, pedestrian, sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:14.61,0:34:16.61,Default,,0,0,0,,They get the pedestrian
Dialogue: 0,0:34:16.61,0:34:18.61,Default,,0,0,0,,limited content,
Dialogue: 0,0:34:18.61,0:34:20.61,Default,,0,0,0,,but they don't get the meaning.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:20.61,0:34:22.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Therefore, what does it mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:22.61,0:34:24.61,Default,,0,0,0,,They don't know what it means, because
Dialogue: 0,0:34:24.61,0:34:26.67,Default,,0,0,0,,the mind at that point
Dialogue: 0,0:34:26.67,0:34:28.67,Default,,0,0,0,,has not reached the capacity
Dialogue: 0,0:34:28.67,0:34:30.67,Default,,0,0,0,,of abstraction.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:30.67,0:34:32.67,Default,,0,0,0,,So, abstract thought
Dialogue: 0,0:34:32.67,0:34:34.67,Default,,0,0,0,,is of a higher level than concrete
Dialogue: 0,0:34:34.67,0:34:36.67,Default,,0,0,0,,mundane thought.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:36.67,0:34:38.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Provability has nothing to do with meaning.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:38.67,0:34:40.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Meaning is an
Dialogue: 0,0:34:40.71,0:34:42.71,Default,,0,0,0,,abstract. So, meaning has to
Dialogue: 0,0:34:42.71,0:34:44.71,Default,,0,0,0,,do with the context, contextual
Dialogue: 0,0:34:44.71,0:34:46.71,Default,,0,0,0,,understanding of the significance of the
Dialogue: 0,0:34:46.71,0:34:48.75,Default,,0,0,0,,meaning. And much of
Dialogue: 0,0:34:48.75,0:34:50.75,Default,,0,0,0,,spiritual work is the revelation
Dialogue: 0,0:34:50.75,0:34:52.75,Default,,0,0,0,,constantly of significance and meaning.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:52.75,0:34:54.75,Default,,0,0,0,,You say, God, what does that mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:54.75,0:34:56.75,Default,,0,0,0,,What is the inference? And then suddenly
Dialogue: 0,0:34:56.75,0:34:58.75,Default,,0,0,0,,you stand
Dialogue: 0,0:34:58.75,0:35:00.75,Default,,0,0,0,,back and you suddenly get, oh wow,
Dialogue: 0,0:35:00.75,0:35:02.75,Default,,0,0,0,,you suddenly see the significance of
Dialogue: 0,0:35:02.75,0:35:04.75,Default,,0,0,0,,the whole thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:04.75,0:35:06.75,Default,,0,0,0,,And if you were going to explain this to somebody,
Dialogue: 0,0:35:06.75,0:35:08.75,Default,,0,0,0,,else you would find it difficult, because
Dialogue: 0,0:35:08.75,0:35:10.75,Default,,0,0,0,,how can you put the non-linear
Dialogue: 0,0:35:10.75,0:35:12.75,Default,,0,0,0,,into a linear content? That's been the
Dialogue: 0,0:35:12.75,0:35:15.19,Default,,0,0,0,,trouble with describing
Dialogue: 0,0:35:15.19,0:35:17.19,Default,,0,0,0,,spiritual truth throughout the ages.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:17.19,0:35:19.19,Default,,0,0,0,,How can you put the non-linear into
Dialogue: 0,0:35:19.19,0:35:21.19,Default,,0,0,0,,language when language is
Dialogue: 0,0:35:21.19,0:35:23.19,Default,,0,0,0,,primarily linear?
Dialogue: 0,0:35:23.19,0:35:25.19,Default,,0,0,0,,So, you speak of the ineffable,
Dialogue: 0,0:35:25.19,0:35:27.44,Default,,0,0,0,,you speak
Dialogue: 0,0:35:27.44,0:35:29.44,Default,,0,0,0,,of the mystical.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:29.44,0:35:31.55,Default,,0,0,0,,The mystic is
Dialogue: 0,0:35:31.55,0:35:33.55,Default,,0,0,0,,one whose consciousness
Dialogue: 0,0:35:33.55,0:35:35.55,Default,,0,0,0,,is dominated by a field,
Dialogue: 0,0:35:35.55,0:35:37.92,Default,,0,0,0,,not by
Dialogue: 0,0:35:37.92,0:35:39.92,Default,,0,0,0,,the content of the field, but by the field
Dialogue: 0,0:35:39.92,0:35:42.15,Default,,0,0,0,,itself, by which
Dialogue: 0,0:35:42.15,0:35:44.15,Default,,0,0,0,,everything is recontextualized,
Dialogue: 0,0:35:44.15,0:35:46.53,Default,,0,0,0,,yes? So,
Dialogue: 0,0:35:46.53,0:35:48.53,Default,,0,0,0,,truth is an abstraction.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:48.53,0:35:50.53,Default,,0,0,0,,So, you can take facts
Dialogue: 0,0:35:50.53,0:35:52.53,Default,,0,0,0,,and then from these facts you get meaning
Dialogue: 0,0:35:52.53,0:35:54.53,Default,,0,0,0,,and then you get
Dialogue: 0,0:35:54.53,0:35:56.53,Default,,0,0,0,,what is the truth of this, you see?
Dialogue: 0,0:35:56.53,0:35:58.53,Default,,0,0,0,,So, truth is a higher level of
Dialogue: 0,0:35:58.53,0:36:01.30,Default,,0,0,0,,abstraction. So, in the great books
Dialogue: 0,0:36:01.30,0:36:03.30,Default,,0,0,0,,of the Western world, you see,
Dialogue: 0,0:36:03.30,0:36:05.30,Default,,0,0,0,,the various levels
Dialogue: 0,0:36:05.30,0:36:07.30,Default,,0,0,0,,of comprehension are laid out pretty
Dialogue: 0,0:36:07.30,0:36:09.34,Default,,0,0,0,,much, you see? There's
Dialogue: 0,0:36:09.34,0:36:11.34,Default,,0,0,0,,the concrete, the literal, then there's
Dialogue: 0,0:36:11.34,0:36:13.34,Default,,0,0,0,,the inference, and then the higher
Dialogue: 0,0:36:13.34,0:36:15.34,Default,,0,0,0,,and higher levels of abstract
Dialogue: 0,0:36:15.34,0:36:17.34,Default,,0,0,0,,truth. The Kant, you know,
Dialogue: 0,0:36:17.34,0:36:19.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Kant, Manuel Kant's
Dialogue: 0,0:36:19.34,0:36:21.34,Default,,0,0,0,,levels of categories. And what you see
Dialogue: 0,0:36:21.34,0:36:23.34,Default,,0,0,0,,with relativism, for instance,
Dialogue: 0,0:36:23.34,0:36:25.34,Default,,0,0,0,,is there's no respect
Dialogue: 0,0:36:25.34,0:36:27.34,Default,,0,0,0,,for categories. They think
Dialogue: 0,0:36:27.34,0:36:29.34,Default,,0,0,0,,you can just, you know, mix one category
Dialogue: 0,0:36:29.34,0:36:31.34,Default,,0,0,0,,with another one because it suits your political
Dialogue: 0,0:36:31.34,0:36:33.34,Default,,0,0,0,,purpose. And
Dialogue: 0,0:36:33.34,0:36:35.34,Default,,0,0,0,,the laws of logic are you cannot
Dialogue: 0,0:36:35.34,0:36:37.34,Default,,0,0,0,,mix levels, you cannot mix levels.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:37.34,0:36:39.34,Default,,0,0,0,,What is true on one level is not true
Dialogue: 0,0:36:39.34,0:36:41.34,Default,,0,0,0,,on another level. What is true
Dialogue: 0,0:36:41.34,0:36:43.34,Default,,0,0,0,,on one level is not true on another level.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:43.34,0:36:45.44,Default,,0,0,0,,And so, one error
Dialogue: 0,0:36:45.44,0:36:47.44,Default,,0,0,0,,that people do make,
Dialogue: 0,0:36:47.44,0:36:49.44,Default,,0,0,0,,you know, especially critics of spiritual work,
Dialogue: 0,0:36:49.44,0:36:51.50,Default,,0,0,0,,is they don't respect
Dialogue: 0,0:36:51.50,0:36:53.50,Default,,0,0,0,,the Kantian categories,
Dialogue: 0,0:36:53.50,0:36:55.50,Default,,0,0,0,,levels of abstraction of
Dialogue: 0,0:36:55.50,0:36:57.50,Default,,0,0,0,,truth and logic.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:57.50,0:37:00.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Everything is only true at
Dialogue: 0,0:37:00.03,0:37:02.03,Default,,0,0,0,,its own level.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:02.03,0:37:04.13,Default,,0,0,0,,So, to make
Dialogue: 0,0:37:04.13,0:37:06.13,Default,,0,0,0,,it wrong, what is done politically is to
Dialogue: 0,0:37:06.13,0:37:08.13,Default,,0,0,0,,take it from this level, put it in this level,
Dialogue: 0,0:37:08.13,0:37:10.13,Default,,0,0,0,,and then do a make wrong on it.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:10.13,0:37:13.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:13.44,0:37:15.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Does that explain it well enough? Yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:37:15.44,0:37:18.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Probably the explanation is more
Dialogue: 0,0:37:18.69,0:37:20.69,Default,,0,0,0,,complicated than the
Dialogue: 0,0:37:20.69,0:37:22.69,Default,,0,0,0,,presentation to begin with.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:22.69,0:37:26.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, ma'am?
Dialogue: 0,0:37:28.55,0:37:48.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:48.09,0:37:50.09,Default,,0,0,0,,It sometimes is very critical to life.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:50.09,0:37:52.09,Default,,0,0,0,,As I just said, your very
Dialogue: 0,0:37:52.09,0:37:54.69,Default,,0,0,0,,existence is currently under threat.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:54.69,0:37:56.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Your existence is not guaranteed
Dialogue: 0,0:37:56.69,0:37:58.88,Default,,0,0,0,,whatsoever.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:58.88,0:38:00.88,Default,,0,0,0,,And it's because of a compartmentalized
Dialogue: 0,0:38:00.88,0:38:02.88,Default,,0,0,0,,split personality. So,
Dialogue: 0,0:38:02.88,0:38:04.88,Default,,0,0,0,,it is very critical.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:04.88,0:38:07.88,Default,,0,0,0,,And the only way
Dialogue: 0,0:38:07.88,0:38:09.88,Default,,0,0,0,,I know to diagnose it
Dialogue: 0,0:38:09.88,0:38:11.88,Default,,0,0,0,,is to begin to suspect it, that there seems
Dialogue: 0,0:38:11.88,0:38:13.88,Default,,0,0,0,,to be two sides to this person's personality.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:13.88,0:38:15.88,Default,,0,0,0,,There seems to be a puzzlement.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:15.88,0:38:17.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Sometimes the people
Dialogue: 0,0:38:17.88,0:38:19.88,Default,,0,0,0,,are aware of it, sometimes they're not.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:22.07,0:38:24.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Great disparities in behaviors
Dialogue: 0,0:38:24.07,0:38:26.07,Default,,0,0,0,,and the unexpected.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:26.07,0:38:28.42,Default,,0,0,0,,It comes about
Dialogue: 0,0:38:28.42,0:38:30.42,Default,,0,0,0,,really from clinical sophistication
Dialogue: 0,0:38:30.42,0:38:32.42,Default,,0,0,0,,to begin to suspect it, frankly.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:32.42,0:38:34.42,Default,,0,0,0,,First of all, you have to even know
Dialogue: 0,0:38:34.42,0:38:36.42,Default,,0,0,0,,that it exists and that it's a very
Dialogue: 0,0:38:36.42,0:38:38.42,Default,,0,0,0,,important thing to know at times.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:40.80,0:38:42.80,Default,,0,0,0,,To even know that it exists.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:42.80,0:38:44.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Compartmentalized personalities.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:44.80,0:38:46.80,Default,,0,0,0,,We know, pretty much everybody's
Dialogue: 0,0:38:46.80,0:38:48.80,Default,,0,0,0,,heard about multiple personalities.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:48.80,0:38:50.80,Default,,0,0,0,,But, you know,
Dialogue: 0,0:38:50.80,0:38:52.80,Default,,0,0,0,,a very discrete split personality
Dialogue: 0,0:38:52.80,0:38:54.80,Default,,0,0,0,,is very often
Dialogue: 0,0:38:54.80,0:38:56.80,Default,,0,0,0,,between one that calibrates very low
Dialogue: 0,0:38:56.80,0:38:58.80,Default,,0,0,0,,and the other one calibrates high.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:58.80,0:39:00.80,Default,,0,0,0,,It's like the angelic and the
Dialogue: 0,0:39:00.80,0:39:02.80,Default,,0,0,0,,demonic were both heading for this body
Dialogue: 0,0:39:02.80,0:39:04.80,Default,,0,0,0,,and they both got there at the same time
Dialogue: 0,0:39:04.80,0:39:06.80,Default,,0,0,0,,somehow.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:06.80,0:39:08.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Two spirits
Dialogue: 0,0:39:08.80,0:39:10.80,Default,,0,0,0,,in only one body.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:10.80,0:39:12.80,Default,,0,0,0,,So I'm sure there's peculiar karmic propensities
Dialogue: 0,0:39:12.80,0:39:14.80,Default,,0,0,0,,which I don't know and I've never
Dialogue: 0,0:39:14.80,0:39:16.80,Default,,0,0,0,,researched.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:16.80,0:39:18.80,Default,,0,0,0,,As I say, the split personalities I've known
Dialogue: 0,0:39:18.80,0:39:20.80,Default,,0,0,0,,in my personal life have been very unpleasant,
Dialogue: 0,0:39:20.80,0:39:22.80,Default,,0,0,0,,frankly, because they get into your life
Dialogue: 0,0:39:22.80,0:39:24.80,Default,,0,0,0,,with their benign, isn't he a wonderful person
Dialogue: 0,0:39:24.80,0:39:26.80,Default,,0,0,0,,and the next thing you know
Dialogue: 0,0:39:26.80,0:39:28.80,Default,,0,0,0,,they're putting a knife in your back
Dialogue: 0,0:39:28.80,0:39:30.80,Default,,0,0,0,,and you never suspected it.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:30.80,0:39:32.80,Default,,0,0,0,,They can have a very, very, very
Dialogue: 0,0:39:32.80,0:39:34.80,Default,,0,0,0,,devastating effect on your life.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:34.80,0:39:37.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, very devastating.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:37.63,0:39:39.76,Default,,0,0,0,,And
Dialogue: 0,0:39:39.76,0:39:41.76,Default,,0,0,0,,very often it's met with denial.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:41.76,0:39:43.76,Default,,0,0,0,,They'll say that, you know, so and so
Dialogue: 0,0:39:43.76,0:39:45.84,Default,,0,0,0,,and then they give you
Dialogue: 0,0:39:45.84,0:39:47.84,Default,,0,0,0,,some reading on their negative side
Dialogue: 0,0:39:47.84,0:39:49.84,Default,,0,0,0,,and you say, oh no, oh no,
Dialogue: 0,0:39:49.84,0:39:51.84,Default,,0,0,0,,because you're so sure the way your perception
Dialogue: 0,0:39:51.84,0:39:53.84,Default,,0,0,0,,is correct.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:53.84,0:39:55.84,Default,,0,0,0,,So you always hold in mind that there could be an alternate side
Dialogue: 0,0:39:55.84,0:39:57.84,Default,,0,0,0,,to a personality
Dialogue: 0,0:39:57.84,0:39:59.84,Default,,0,0,0,,and they're not always
Dialogue: 0,0:39:59.84,0:40:02.03,Default,,0,0,0,,the same person.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:02.03,0:40:04.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:04.09,0:40:09.00,Default,,0,0,0,,During the lecture you spoke of the experiencer.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:09.00,0:40:25.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:25.82,0:40:27.82,Default,,0,0,0,,No, you just become the witness
Dialogue: 0,0:40:27.82,0:40:29.94,Default,,0,0,0,,of the experiencer.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:29.94,0:40:31.98,Default,,0,0,0,,The experiencer is
Dialogue: 0,0:40:31.98,0:40:33.98,Default,,0,0,0,,tries to milk everything
Dialogue: 0,0:40:33.98,0:40:36.03,Default,,0,0,0,,to ensure its own survivor.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:36.03,0:40:38.03,Default,,0,0,0,,You become the witness
Dialogue: 0,0:40:38.03,0:40:40.11,Default,,0,0,0,,of the ego doing that.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:40.11,0:40:42.11,Default,,0,0,0,,You become the witness
Dialogue: 0,0:40:42.11,0:40:44.11,Default,,0,0,0,,of the observer. So you're detached
Dialogue: 0,0:40:44.11,0:40:46.11,Default,,0,0,0,,then from subjectively
Dialogue: 0,0:40:46.11,0:40:48.11,Default,,0,0,0,,identifying yourself with the experiencer.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:48.11,0:40:50.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Ordinarily the mind
Dialogue: 0,0:40:50.17,0:40:52.17,Default,,0,0,0,,thinks, well I am that which is
Dialogue: 0,0:40:52.17,0:40:54.17,Default,,0,0,0,,experiencing.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:54.17,0:40:56.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Instead of I am the consciousness,
Dialogue: 0,0:40:56.17,0:40:58.17,Default,,0,0,0,,the observer, the witness
Dialogue: 0,0:40:58.17,0:41:00.17,Default,,0,0,0,,of the phenomena.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:02.17,0:41:04.17,Default,,0,0,0,,You're more detached when you see
Dialogue: 0,0:41:04.17,0:41:06.17,Default,,0,0,0,,yourself as the witness observer.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:06.17,0:41:08.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Then how do you know
Dialogue: 0,0:41:08.26,0:41:10.26,Default,,0,0,0,,that you're the witness observer?
Dialogue: 0,0:41:10.26,0:41:12.26,Default,,0,0,0,,The witness observer then is coming out
Dialogue: 0,0:41:12.26,0:41:14.26,Default,,0,0,0,,of the consciousness itself.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:14.26,0:41:16.30,Default,,0,0,0,,It's because of consciousness
Dialogue: 0,0:41:16.30,0:41:18.30,Default,,0,0,0,,itself that you're capable
Dialogue: 0,0:41:18.30,0:41:20.30,Default,,0,0,0,,of having a witness observer.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:20.30,0:41:22.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Much less an experiencer.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:22.30,0:41:24.75,Default,,0,0,0,,To have no thought
Dialogue: 0,0:41:24.75,0:41:26.75,Default,,0,0,0,,about what goes on.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:26.75,0:41:28.88,Default,,0,0,0,,It comes about
Dialogue: 0,0:41:28.88,0:41:30.88,Default,,0,0,0,,through a contemplative lifestyle.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:30.88,0:41:33.15,Default,,0,0,0,,So that you end up
Dialogue: 0,0:41:33.15,0:41:35.15,Default,,0,0,0,,thinking about a thing
Dialogue: 0,0:41:35.15,0:41:37.15,Default,,0,0,0,,only if you choose to think about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:37.15,0:41:39.32,Default,,0,0,0,,If you say, well I think
Dialogue: 0,0:41:39.32,0:41:41.32,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll think about this, then you think about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:41.32,0:41:43.32,Default,,0,0,0,,But you don't think about it
Dialogue: 0,0:41:43.32,0:41:45.32,Default,,0,0,0,,against
Dialogue: 0,0:41:45.32,0:41:47.42,Default,,0,0,0,,your own choice.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:47.42,0:41:49.48,Default,,0,0,0,,So that comes about
Dialogue: 0,0:41:49.48,0:41:51.48,Default,,0,0,0,,as a contemplative lifestyle
Dialogue: 0,0:41:51.48,0:41:54.05,Default,,0,0,0,,where the field
Dialogue: 0,0:41:54.05,0:41:56.05,Default,,0,0,0,,is aware of the content of the field
Dialogue: 0,0:41:56.05,0:41:58.05,Default,,0,0,0,,but it's aware
Dialogue: 0,0:41:58.05,0:42:00.05,Default,,0,0,0,,only out of its being a field.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:00.05,0:42:02.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Not out of its being
Dialogue: 0,0:42:02.05,0:42:04.19,Default,,0,0,0,,a particular you.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:04.19,0:42:06.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Just as what's being said now
Dialogue: 0,0:42:06.19,0:42:08.19,Default,,0,0,0,,is being witnessed. I have no idea what he's talking about.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:08.19,0:42:11.30,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:11.30,0:42:13.50,Default,,0,0,0,,I hear it the same time you hear it.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:13.50,0:42:15.50,Default,,0,0,0,,The speakingness happens
Dialogue: 0,0:42:15.50,0:42:17.50,Default,,0,0,0,,of its own spontaneity
Dialogue: 0,0:42:17.50,0:42:19.50,Default,,0,0,0,,as the speakingness
Dialogue: 0,0:42:19.50,0:42:21.50,Default,,0,0,0,,because that's an attribute
Dialogue: 0,0:42:21.50,0:42:23.50,Default,,0,0,0,,that you relearn
Dialogue: 0,0:42:23.50,0:42:25.92,Default,,0,0,0,,after you
Dialogue: 0,0:42:25.92,0:42:27.92,Default,,0,0,0,,lose the ability to relate to the world.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:27.92,0:42:30.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Slowly over time
Dialogue: 0,0:42:30.42,0:42:32.42,Default,,0,0,0,,you relearn
Dialogue: 0,0:42:32.42,0:42:34.51,Default,,0,0,0,,and I call that
Dialogue: 0,0:42:34.51,0:42:36.51,Default,,0,0,0,,persona. There's an aspect
Dialogue: 0,0:42:36.51,0:42:38.51,Default,,0,0,0,,of consciousness which then learns
Dialogue: 0,0:42:38.51,0:42:40.51,Default,,0,0,0,,to interact with the world
Dialogue: 0,0:42:40.51,0:42:42.78,Default,,0,0,0,,and converse with it
Dialogue: 0,0:42:42.78,0:42:44.78,Default,,0,0,0,,and know which streetcar to get onto and all that.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:44.78,0:42:46.78,Default,,0,0,0,,But it has nothing to do with who you are.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:46.78,0:42:48.78,Default,,0,0,0,,You're the witness.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:48.78,0:42:50.78,Default,,0,0,0,,It could be just somebody else in another body.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:50.78,0:42:52.78,Default,,0,0,0,,It doesn't have any personal
Dialogue: 0,0:42:52.78,0:42:54.94,Default,,0,0,0,,meaning anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:54.94,0:42:56.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Therefore whether you're
Dialogue: 0,0:42:56.94,0:42:58.94,Default,,0,0,0,,good or bad, you know,
Dialogue: 0,0:42:58.94,0:43:00.94,Default,,0,0,0,,it's the other person's problem
Dialogue: 0,0:43:00.94,0:43:02.94,Default,,0,0,0,,because it's their perception
Dialogue: 0,0:43:02.94,0:43:04.94,Default,,0,0,0,,and it's got nothing to do with your own reality
Dialogue: 0,0:43:04.94,0:43:06.94,Default,,0,0,0,,which is beyond good and bad, etc.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:06.94,0:43:08.96,Default,,0,0,0,,You don't know
Dialogue: 0,0:43:08.96,0:43:10.96,Default,,0,0,0,,who they're talking about.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:10.96,0:43:12.96,Default,,0,0,0,,So as I say,
Dialogue: 0,0:43:12.96,0:43:14.96,Default,,0,0,0,,when that state first emerged
Dialogue: 0,0:43:14.96,0:43:16.96,Default,,0,0,0,,I would see people
Dialogue: 0,0:43:16.96,0:43:18.96,Default,,0,0,0,,talking to this body
Dialogue: 0,0:43:18.96,0:43:20.96,Default,,0,0,0,,and I couldn't figure
Dialogue: 0,0:43:20.96,0:43:23.51,Default,,0,0,0,,who they're talking to.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:23.51,0:43:25.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Who the hell is he talking to?
Dialogue: 0,0:43:25.51,0:43:27.51,Default,,0,0,0,,And I realized they think it's me.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:27.51,0:43:33.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:33.03,0:43:35.03,Default,,0,0,0,,I couldn't figure out who they're talking to.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:35.03,0:43:37.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Who are they talking to?
Dialogue: 0,0:43:37.03,0:43:39.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Because the body had nothing to do
Dialogue: 0,0:43:39.03,0:43:41.03,Default,,0,0,0,,with who I am
Dialogue: 0,0:43:41.03,0:43:43.26,Default,,0,0,0,,or even where I was, you might say.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:43.26,0:43:45.26,Default,,0,0,0,,The consciousness may be here
Dialogue: 0,0:43:45.26,0:43:47.26,Default,,0,0,0,,and here's Doc's body over here
Dialogue: 0,0:43:47.26,0:43:49.26,Default,,0,0,0,,and people are talking to this thing here.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:49.26,0:43:51.26,Default,,0,0,0,,What the hell are they talking to?
Dialogue: 0,0:43:51.26,0:43:53.67,Default,,0,0,0,,You know what I'm saying?
Dialogue: 0,0:43:53.67,0:43:55.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Like out of body, I'm here
Dialogue: 0,0:43:55.67,0:43:57.67,Default,,0,0,0,,and they're talking to this body here
Dialogue: 0,0:43:57.67,0:43:59.67,Default,,0,0,0,,and that's certainly a strange phenomenon.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:01.67,0:44:04.09,Default,,0,0,0,,It took a while
Dialogue: 0,0:44:04.09,0:44:06.11,Default,,0,0,0,,for people to realize
Dialogue: 0,0:44:06.11,0:44:08.11,Default,,0,0,0,,that they're talking to that
Dialogue: 0,0:44:08.11,0:44:10.11,Default,,0,0,0,,and that is what they assumed to be you.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:10.11,0:44:12.11,Default,,0,0,0,,So then you learn how to
Dialogue: 0,0:44:12.11,0:44:14.11,Default,,0,0,0,,via the persona
Dialogue: 0,0:44:14.11,0:44:16.11,Default,,0,0,0,,become that entity
Dialogue: 0,0:44:16.11,0:44:18.11,Default,,0,0,0,,to the degree that is necessary
Dialogue: 0,0:44:18.11,0:44:20.11,Default,,0,0,0,,in a social interaction.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:20.11,0:44:22.11,Default,,0,0,0,,If there's no necessity
Dialogue: 0,0:44:22.11,0:44:24.11,Default,,0,0,0,,for social interaction
Dialogue: 0,0:44:24.11,0:44:26.11,Default,,0,0,0,,there's no necessity
Dialogue: 0,0:44:26.11,0:44:28.11,Default,,0,0,0,,to own that persona.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:28.11,0:44:30.11,Default,,0,0,0,,It would just be excess baggage
Dialogue: 0,0:44:30.11,0:44:32.59,Default,,0,0,0,,like you don't need a raincoat
Dialogue: 0,0:44:32.59,0:44:34.59,Default,,0,0,0,,if it's not raining.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:34.59,0:44:36.59,Default,,0,0,0,,The phenomena sort of grew out of themselves.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:36.59,0:44:38.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't forget there isn't any book on such a matter.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:38.59,0:44:40.59,Default,,0,0,0,,And it was just discovered
Dialogue: 0,0:44:40.59,0:44:42.59,Default,,0,0,0,,through a personal
Dialogue: 0,0:44:42.59,0:44:44.59,Default,,0,0,0,,what the Rokoff's personal
Dialogue: 0,0:44:44.59,0:44:46.59,Default,,0,0,0,,subject of awareness
Dialogue: 0,0:44:46.59,0:44:48.59,Default,,0,0,0,,the learning of these things.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:48.59,0:44:50.82,Default,,0,0,0,,They may be somewhere
Dialogue: 0,0:44:50.82,0:44:52.82,Default,,0,0,0,,in some book
Dialogue: 0,0:44:52.82,0:44:54.96,Default,,0,0,0,,but I've never read it.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:54.96,0:45:02.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:45:02.13,0:45:04.13,Default,,0,0,0,,I need somebody to translate
Dialogue: 0,0:45:04.13,0:45:08.63,Default,,0,0,0,,what he says.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:08.63,0:45:13.67,Default,,0,0,0,,With what?
Dialogue: 0,0:45:13.67,0:45:15.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Well this persona interacts with
Dialogue: 0,0:45:15.67,0:45:17.67,Default,,0,0,0,,everything.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:17.67,0:45:21.11,Default,,0,0,0,,It will say something
Dialogue: 0,0:45:21.11,0:45:23.11,Default,,0,0,0,,but it is
Dialogue: 0,0:45:23.11,0:45:25.53,Default,,0,0,0,,it will say something
Dialogue: 0,0:45:25.53,0:45:27.53,Default,,0,0,0,,but it's because
Dialogue: 0,0:45:27.53,0:45:29.53,Default,,0,0,0,,that's the conversational
Dialogue: 0,0:45:29.53,0:45:31.65,Default,,0,0,0,,interaction of the moment.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:31.65,0:45:33.65,Default,,0,0,0,,It has no intrinsic
Dialogue: 0,0:45:33.65,0:45:35.65,Default,,0,0,0,,great reality.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:35.65,0:45:37.65,Default,,0,0,0,,So
Dialogue: 0,0:45:37.65,0:45:39.92,Default,,0,0,0,,because of the alignment
Dialogue: 0,0:45:39.92,0:45:41.92,Default,,0,0,0,,and the lovingness between the two
Dialogue: 0,0:45:41.92,0:45:43.92,Default,,0,0,0,,everything becomes
Dialogue: 0,0:45:43.92,0:45:45.92,Default,,0,0,0,,recontextualized.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:45.92,0:45:47.92,Default,,0,0,0,,So no matter what the person says
Dialogue: 0,0:45:47.92,0:45:49.92,Default,,0,0,0,,it doesn't have any
Dialogue: 0,0:45:49.92,0:45:51.92,Default,,0,0,0,,effect on the alignment
Dialogue: 0,0:45:51.92,0:45:53.92,Default,,0,0,0,,whatsoever.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:53.92,0:45:55.92,Default,,0,0,0,,A person could be angry at you one second
Dialogue: 0,0:45:55.92,0:45:57.92,Default,,0,0,0,,and it doesn't really mean anything
Dialogue: 0,0:45:57.92,0:45:59.92,Default,,0,0,0,,because in two seconds later it's gone.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:59.92,0:46:02.01,Default,,0,0,0,,If something was going to
Dialogue: 0,0:46:02.01,0:46:04.01,Default,,0,0,0,,threaten the relationship
Dialogue: 0,0:46:04.01,0:46:06.01,Default,,0,0,0,,that would have a different impact.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:06.01,0:46:08.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Because your alignment is a commitment
Dialogue: 0,0:46:08.01,0:46:10.01,Default,,0,0,0,,you're both aligned
Dialogue: 0,0:46:10.01,0:46:12.01,Default,,0,0,0,,and committed to reach God
Dialogue: 0,0:46:12.01,0:46:14.01,Default,,0,0,0,,so that makes you parallels.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:14.01,0:46:16.94,Default,,0,0,0,,You know
Dialogue: 0,0:46:16.94,0:46:18.94,Default,,0,0,0,,a little static on the radio
Dialogue: 0,0:46:18.94,0:46:20.94,Default,,0,0,0,,is not exactly a major transmission
Dialogue: 0,0:46:20.94,0:46:22.94,Default,,0,0,0,,at all times.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:22.94,0:46:24.94,Default,,0,0,0,,You know what I'm saying?
Dialogue: 0,0:46:24.94,0:46:26.94,Default,,0,0,0,,You can say something
Dialogue: 0,0:46:26.94,0:46:28.94,Default,,0,0,0,,back and forth
Dialogue: 0,0:46:28.94,0:46:30.94,Default,,0,0,0,,out of your animalness.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:30.94,0:46:32.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't forget you're an animal.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:32.94,0:46:34.94,Default,,0,0,0,,So the cause for
Dialogue: 0,0:46:34.94,0:46:37.32,Default,,0,0,0,,disparity is really your animal.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:37.32,0:46:39.44,Default,,0,0,0,,It's really your animal.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:39.44,0:46:41.76,Default,,0,0,0,,And I'll say now
Dialogue: 0,0:46:41.76,0:46:43.76,Default,,0,0,0,,my animal will go in the refrigerator
Dialogue: 0,0:46:43.76,0:46:45.76,Default,,0,0,0,,and I say
Dialogue: 0,0:46:45.76,0:46:48.40,Default,,0,0,0,,where in the world is the pickled herring?
Dialogue: 0,0:46:48.40,0:46:53.07,Default,,0,0,0,,And her animal
Dialogue: 0,0:46:53.07,0:46:55.07,Default,,0,0,0,,will come up and say
Dialogue: 0,0:46:55.07,0:46:57.07,Default,,0,0,0,,right here in front of your eyes.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:57.07,0:47:05.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Alright, alright.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:05.17,0:47:07.17,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't want to mix it up.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:07.17,0:47:09.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Get a pickled herring
Dialogue: 0,0:47:09.82,0:47:11.82,Default,,0,0,0,,right in your eye.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:11.82,0:47:14.03,Default,,0,0,0,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:14.03,0:47:16.03,Default,,0,0,0,,It's never physical.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:16.03,0:47:18.03,Default,,0,0,0,,It's just the nuisance
Dialogue: 0,0:47:18.03,0:47:20.03,Default,,0,0,0,,the annoyance.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:20.03,0:47:22.03,Default,,0,0,0,,It's the animal being annoyed.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:22.03,0:47:24.03,Default,,0,0,0,,The animal thinks there's a bone over there
Dialogue: 0,0:47:24.03,0:47:26.03,Default,,0,0,0,,and he goes over there
Dialogue: 0,0:47:26.03,0:47:28.03,Default,,0,0,0,,and the bone falls down the steps
Dialogue: 0,0:47:28.03,0:47:30.03,Default,,0,0,0,,and the animal is annoyed.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:30.03,0:47:32.13,Default,,0,0,0,,It's the animal that's coming up
Dialogue: 0,0:47:32.13,0:47:34.13,Default,,0,0,0,,and not the real you.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:34.13,0:47:36.13,Default,,0,0,0,,The real you hasn't changed any position.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:36.13,0:47:38.13,Default,,0,0,0,,So annoyance I think is between couples
Dialogue: 0,0:47:38.13,0:47:40.13,Default,,0,0,0,,is usually more the animal coming up.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:40.13,0:47:42.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Even the animal coming up.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:42.19,0:47:44.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Even wanting people to agree with you
Dialogue: 0,0:47:44.19,0:47:46.19,Default,,0,0,0,,is really your animal wanting
Dialogue: 0,0:47:46.19,0:47:48.19,Default,,0,0,0,,them they should agree with you all the time.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:48.19,0:47:50.32,Default,,0,0,0,,And
Dialogue: 0,0:47:50.32,0:47:52.32,Default,,0,0,0,,so if you say
Dialogue: 0,0:47:52.32,0:47:54.32,Default,,0,0,0,,well that's just my animal
Dialogue: 0,0:47:54.32,0:47:56.32,Default,,0,0,0,,it's not really who I am you see.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:56.32,0:47:59.38,Default,,0,0,0,,It's not really
Dialogue: 0,0:48:29.61,0:48:31.90,Default,,0,0,0,,So
Dialogue: 0,0:48:31.90,0:48:33.90,Default,,0,0,0,,you end up kidding each other a good deal
Dialogue: 0,0:48:33.90,0:48:36.11,Default,,0,0,0,,you know because
Dialogue: 0,0:48:36.11,0:48:38.11,Default,,0,0,0,,you really do because what would have been
Dialogue: 0,0:48:38.11,0:48:40.11,Default,,0,0,0,,annoying if you kid about it
Dialogue: 0,0:48:40.11,0:48:42.15,Default,,0,0,0,,it defuses it you know what I'm saying.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:42.15,0:48:44.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Somebody ate my last pickled herring well
Dialogue: 0,0:48:44.15,0:48:46.34,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't have to kill them.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:46.34,0:48:49.05,Default,,0,0,0,,I can let them live.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:53.21,0:48:55.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Gave it to the neighbor.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:55.21,0:48:57.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Gave my last pickled herring to the neighbor.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:57.28,0:49:00.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh
Dialogue: 0,0:49:00.42,0:49:02.42,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't have to let go of my attachment
Dialogue: 0,0:49:02.42,0:49:04.94,Default,,0,0,0,,to pickled herring.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:04.94,0:49:06.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Can't get to heaven because you're
Dialogue: 0,0:49:06.94,0:49:09.28,Default,,0,0,0,,attached to pickled herring.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:11.28,0:49:13.28,Default,,0,0,0,,God says you love me more
Dialogue: 0,0:49:13.28,0:49:15.55,Default,,0,0,0,,or pickled herring more.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:15.55,0:49:17.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Alright
Dialogue: 0,0:49:17.55,0:49:19.55,Default,,0,0,0,,What else needs clarification?
Dialogue: 0,0:49:19.55,0:49:24.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes indeed sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:24.19,0:49:27.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:27.42,0:49:45.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:45.57,0:49:47.57,Default,,0,0,0,,You see if you come from right and wrong
Dialogue: 0,0:49:47.57,0:49:49.57,Default,,0,0,0,,you'd say well gee that's terrible
Dialogue: 0,0:49:49.57,0:49:51.57,Default,,0,0,0,,they're lying all the time. But that's their job.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:51.57,0:49:55.53,Default,,0,0,0,,If I ask
Dialogue: 0,0:49:55.53,0:49:57.53,Default,,0,0,0,,about specifically let's see
Dialogue: 0,0:49:57.53,0:49:59.55,Default,,0,0,0,,I have specifically
Dialogue: 0,0:49:59.55,0:50:02.19,Default,,0,0,0,,have permission to ask about
Dialogue: 0,0:50:02.19,0:50:04.80,Default,,0,0,0,,the U.N. resist.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:04.80,0:50:06.80,Default,,0,0,0,,The politicians in the U.N.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:06.80,0:50:08.80,Default,,0,0,0,,lie routinely resist.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:08.80,0:50:12.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Routinely.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:12.28,0:50:14.28,Default,,0,0,0,,You know the U.N. calibrates at 190.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:14.28,0:50:16.38,Default,,0,0,0,,If they were telling the truth
Dialogue: 0,0:50:16.38,0:50:18.38,Default,,0,0,0,,all the time it would be like 420 wouldn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:50:18.38,0:50:21.07,Default,,0,0,0,,So it's
Dialogue: 0,0:50:21.07,0:50:23.07,Default,,0,0,0,,means it's like you're jockeying
Dialogue: 0,0:50:23.07,0:50:25.07,Default,,0,0,0,,for a verbal rhetorical
Dialogue: 0,0:50:25.07,0:50:27.28,Default,,0,0,0,,position.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:27.28,0:50:29.28,Default,,0,0,0,,You're trading
Dialogue: 0,0:50:29.28,0:50:31.28,Default,,0,0,0,,white chips for black chips.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:31.28,0:50:33.28,Default,,0,0,0,,So it's a constant dealing back
Dialogue: 0,0:50:33.28,0:50:35.28,Default,,0,0,0,,and forth. I'll let go
Dialogue: 0,0:50:35.28,0:50:37.28,Default,,0,0,0,,this statement if you let go that
Dialogue: 0,0:50:37.28,0:50:39.28,Default,,0,0,0,,statement and if you give me this advantage
Dialogue: 0,0:50:39.28,0:50:41.28,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll let go this
Dialogue: 0,0:50:41.28,0:50:43.28,Default,,0,0,0,,disadvantage.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:43.28,0:50:45.28,Default,,0,0,0,,It's wheeling and dealing. So you might say
Dialogue: 0,0:50:45.28,0:50:47.28,Default,,0,0,0,,politics is wheeling and dealing
Dialogue: 0,0:50:47.28,0:50:49.28,Default,,0,0,0,,for power and
Dialogue: 0,0:50:49.28,0:50:51.84,Default,,0,0,0,,the gain. Whatever
Dialogue: 0,0:50:51.84,0:50:53.84,Default,,0,0,0,,gain they presume occurs.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:53.84,0:50:55.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Right now the primary gain
Dialogue: 0,0:50:55.84,0:50:57.84,Default,,0,0,0,,is number one oil
Dialogue: 0,0:50:57.84,0:50:59.84,Default,,0,0,0,,money and number two moral
Dialogue: 0,0:50:59.84,0:51:01.84,Default,,0,0,0,,high ground.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:01.84,0:51:05.07,Default,,0,0,0,,You hear all these
Dialogue: 0,0:51:05.07,0:51:07.07,Default,,0,0,0,,political arguments they're all about the moral
Dialogue: 0,0:51:07.07,0:51:09.61,Default,,0,0,0,,high ground.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:09.61,0:51:11.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Moral high ground and with it often
Dialogue: 0,0:51:11.61,0:51:13.61,Default,,0,0,0,,goes the money with the oil.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:13.61,0:51:16.40,Default,,0,0,0,,So that has to do with survival.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:16.40,0:51:18.40,Default,,0,0,0,,So the politician is interested
Dialogue: 0,0:51:18.40,0:51:20.40,Default,,0,0,0,,in survival and
Dialogue: 0,0:51:20.40,0:51:22.40,Default,,0,0,0,,primarily survival of his own position.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:22.40,0:51:24.40,Default,,0,0,0,,His own position.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:24.40,0:51:26.40,Default,,0,0,0,,You see people switch sides depending on which
Dialogue: 0,0:51:26.40,0:51:28.40,Default,,0,0,0,,is popular. If this gets more votes
Dialogue: 0,0:51:28.40,0:51:30.40,Default,,0,0,0,,suddenly they go in this way. When this gets more votes
Dialogue: 0,0:51:30.40,0:51:32.53,Default,,0,0,0,,they go this way.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:32.53,0:51:34.53,Default,,0,0,0,,So you might say that's not a defect
Dialogue: 0,0:51:34.53,0:51:36.53,Default,,0,0,0,,that's his job. That's what he's supposed
Dialogue: 0,0:51:36.53,0:51:39.30,Default,,0,0,0,,to do. If you find more people
Dialogue: 0,0:51:39.30,0:51:41.30,Default,,0,0,0,,like chocolate than vanilla somehow
Dialogue: 0,0:51:41.30,0:51:43.30,Default,,0,0,0,,you begin to favor chocolate don't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:51:45.53,0:51:47.53,Default,,0,0,0,,If you're going to run for president
Dialogue: 0,0:51:47.53,0:51:49.53,Default,,0,0,0,,you can't be for vanilla
Dialogue: 0,0:51:49.53,0:51:51.53,Default,,0,0,0,,when the 55%
Dialogue: 0,0:51:51.53,0:51:53.71,Default,,0,0,0,,prefer chocolate.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:53.71,0:51:55.71,Default,,0,0,0,,So the poll tells you how you got to move
Dialogue: 0,0:51:55.71,0:51:57.71,Default,,0,0,0,,and I think in truth versus false
Dialogue: 0,0:51:57.71,0:51:59.71,Default,,0,0,0,,we calibrated the
Dialogue: 0,0:51:59.71,0:52:01.71,Default,,0,0,0,,various political positions
Dialogue: 0,0:52:01.71,0:52:03.71,Default,,0,0,0,,and the political position of
Dialogue: 0,0:52:03.71,0:52:05.71,Default,,0,0,0,,the electorate. If I remember
Dialogue: 0,0:52:05.71,0:52:07.71,Default,,0,0,0,,the electorate was at about 375.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:07.71,0:52:09.71,Default,,0,0,0,,So for a spiritual platform
Dialogue: 0,0:52:09.71,0:52:11.71,Default,,0,0,0,,to work
Dialogue: 0,0:52:11.71,0:52:13.71,Default,,0,0,0,,they would have to devise it
Dialogue: 0,0:52:13.71,0:52:15.71,Default,,0,0,0,,to appeal to a consciousness level
Dialogue: 0,0:52:15.71,0:52:18.17,Default,,0,0,0,,about 375.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:18.17,0:52:20.17,Default,,0,0,0,,That's why hatred and spite don't really
Dialogue: 0,0:52:20.17,0:52:22.17,Default,,0,0,0,,win elections because that calibrates to 190.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:22.17,0:52:24.17,Default,,0,0,0,,At 375
Dialogue: 0,0:52:24.17,0:52:26.17,Default,,0,0,0,,very few people look favorably
Dialogue: 0,0:52:26.17,0:52:28.17,Default,,0,0,0,,at hatred.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:28.17,0:52:30.17,Default,,0,0,0,,I mean they'll tolerate it
Dialogue: 0,0:52:30.17,0:52:32.17,Default,,0,0,0,,and they'll quote it when they want it
Dialogue: 0,0:52:32.17,0:52:34.17,Default,,0,0,0,,but they don't respect it or vote for it.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:34.17,0:52:36.17,Default,,0,0,0,,So consciousness
Dialogue: 0,0:52:36.17,0:52:38.17,Default,,0,0,0,,level 370 I think was
Dialogue: 0,0:52:38.17,0:52:40.17,Default,,0,0,0,,where the last electorate was.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:40.17,0:52:42.17,Default,,0,0,0,,So if I was devising
Dialogue: 0,0:52:42.17,0:52:44.17,Default,,0,0,0,,a political platform
Dialogue: 0,0:52:44.17,0:52:46.17,Default,,0,0,0,,I would devise one that
Dialogue: 0,0:52:46.17,0:52:48.17,Default,,0,0,0,,appeals to about 375.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:48.17,0:52:50.17,Default,,0,0,0,,That's sort of
Dialogue: 0,0:52:50.17,0:52:52.17,Default,,0,0,0,,middle of the road, whatever is sane
Dialogue: 0,0:52:52.17,0:52:54.17,Default,,0,0,0,,and sensible, whatever sounds ethical
Dialogue: 0,0:52:54.17,0:52:56.26,Default,,0,0,0,,and logical
Dialogue: 0,0:52:56.26,0:52:58.61,Default,,0,0,0,,and sort of
Dialogue: 0,0:52:58.61,0:53:00.61,Default,,0,0,0,,reasonableness
Dialogue: 0,0:53:00.61,0:53:02.61,Default,,0,0,0,,and pretty much good naturedness.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:02.61,0:53:04.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Good natured reasonableness.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:04.61,0:53:06.75,Default,,0,0,0,,So to win an election
Dialogue: 0,0:53:06.75,0:53:08.75,Default,,0,0,0,,I would devise a political platform
Dialogue: 0,0:53:08.75,0:53:10.75,Default,,0,0,0,,and I would calibrate it at 375.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:10.75,0:53:12.75,Default,,0,0,0,,And move my positions around
Dialogue: 0,0:53:12.75,0:53:14.75,Default,,0,0,0,,until they're at 375.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:14.75,0:53:16.84,Default,,0,0,0,,So you can see
Dialogue: 0,0:53:16.84,0:53:18.84,Default,,0,0,0,,even as a politician I would have to
Dialogue: 0,0:53:18.84,0:53:20.84,Default,,0,0,0,,change what I consider to be
Dialogue: 0,0:53:20.84,0:53:22.84,Default,,0,0,0,,sufficiently truthful to present
Dialogue: 0,0:53:22.84,0:53:24.84,Default,,0,0,0,,to the public. Not in order to get elected.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:24.84,0:53:26.88,Default,,0,0,0,,You can't
Dialogue: 0,0:53:26.88,0:53:29.42,Default,,0,0,0,,malign the public
Dialogue: 0,0:53:29.42,0:53:31.42,Default,,0,0,0,,and still get elected.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:31.42,0:53:33.42,Default,,0,0,0,,You're going to have to say what sounds favorable.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:33.42,0:53:35.42,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't think any of them were aware of that.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:35.42,0:53:37.42,Default,,0,0,0,,They struck it by luck.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:37.42,0:53:39.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Clinton I think hit into that.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:39.42,0:53:41.42,Default,,0,0,0,,I think Clinton was in
Dialogue: 0,0:53:41.42,0:53:43.42,Default,,0,0,0,,his platform was around 370 or something.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:43.42,0:53:46.38,Default,,0,0,0,,And he was a big winner.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:46.38,0:53:48.98,Default,,0,0,0,,So avoid the
Dialogue: 0,0:53:48.98,0:53:50.98,Default,,0,0,0,,extremes and try and hit what's
Dialogue: 0,0:53:50.98,0:53:52.98,Default,,0,0,0,,reasonable. 375
Dialogue: 0,0:53:52.98,0:53:54.98,Default,,0,0,0,,and so that's also the appeal
Dialogue: 0,0:53:54.98,0:53:56.98,Default,,0,0,0,,of all the
Dialogue: 0,0:53:56.98,0:53:58.98,Default,,0,0,0,,spiritual books you see in the
Dialogue: 0,0:53:58.98,0:54:00.98,Default,,0,0,0,,truck stops and all. Who's the big
Dialogue: 0,0:54:00.98,0:54:04.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Warren? Rick Warren.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:04.59,0:54:06.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah. You know his
Dialogue: 0,0:54:06.59,0:54:08.59,Default,,0,0,0,,375 that's enthusiasm.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:08.59,0:54:10.59,Default,,0,0,0,,It's 375 that built the
Dialogue: 0,0:54:10.59,0:54:12.59,Default,,0,0,0,,pyramids, that built the Empire State
Dialogue: 0,0:54:12.59,0:54:14.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Building. It's enthusiastic
Dialogue: 0,0:54:14.59,0:54:16.59,Default,,0,0,0,,good heartedness
Dialogue: 0,0:54:16.59,0:54:18.59,Default,,0,0,0,,and enthusiasm.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:18.59,0:54:20.75,Default,,0,0,0,,It's more than just saying yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:20.75,0:54:22.75,Default,,0,0,0,,It's being yes and then being enthusiastic
Dialogue: 0,0:54:22.75,0:54:24.75,Default,,0,0,0,,about the yes and enthusiastic.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:24.75,0:54:26.78,Default,,0,0,0,,So to be enthusiastic
Dialogue: 0,0:54:26.78,0:54:28.78,Default,,0,0,0,,about that which isn't
Dialogue: 0,0:54:28.78,0:54:30.78,Default,,0,0,0,,pretty much almost guarantees success.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:30.78,0:54:32.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Almost guarantees it.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:32.88,0:54:35.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah. And because you're
Dialogue: 0,0:54:35.07,0:54:37.07,Default,,0,0,0,,in a safe level of truth
Dialogue: 0,0:54:37.07,0:54:39.07,Default,,0,0,0,,to begin with you don't have to change your positions
Dialogue: 0,0:54:39.07,0:54:41.07,Default,,0,0,0,,all the time. You don't have to constantly change
Dialogue: 0,0:54:41.07,0:54:43.15,Default,,0,0,0,,position. Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:43.15,0:54:45.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes doc.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:45.15,0:54:53.82,Default,,0,0,0,,You were on the last...
Dialogue: 0,0:54:53.82,0:54:58.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Xeno.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:58.96,0:55:00.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh I don't want you to ask me that.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:00.96,0:55:04.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Xeno you know
Dialogue: 0,0:55:04.80,0:55:06.80,Default,,0,0,0,,the Xeno paradox
Dialogue: 0,0:55:06.80,0:55:08.96,Default,,0,0,0,,was if a
Dialogue: 0,0:55:08.96,0:55:10.96,Default,,0,0,0,,rabbit and a tortoise start out
Dialogue: 0,0:55:10.96,0:55:12.96,Default,,0,0,0,,at the same time
Dialogue: 0,0:55:12.96,0:55:15.00,Default,,0,0,0,,which will win the race you see.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:15.00,0:55:17.00,Default,,0,0,0,,And see the tortoise
Dialogue: 0,0:55:17.00,0:55:19.00,Default,,0,0,0,,goes slower but the thing is
Dialogue: 0,0:55:19.00,0:55:21.00,Default,,0,0,0,,at any point in time
Dialogue: 0,0:55:21.00,0:55:23.00,Default,,0,0,0,,you've only gone half the distance.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:23.00,0:55:25.00,Default,,0,0,0,,And then at the next point in time
Dialogue: 0,0:55:25.00,0:55:27.00,Default,,0,0,0,,you'll again have gone half the distance.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:27.00,0:55:29.00,Default,,0,0,0,,You will then have gone half the distance.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:29.00,0:55:31.00,Default,,0,0,0,,You will then have gone half the distance.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:31.00,0:55:33.00,Default,,0,0,0,,And according to Xeno's paradox
Dialogue: 0,0:55:33.00,0:55:35.00,Default,,0,0,0,,the rabbit never can catch up with the tortoise
Dialogue: 0,0:55:35.00,0:55:37.00,Default,,0,0,0,,because at any point in time
Dialogue: 0,0:55:37.00,0:55:39.00,Default,,0,0,0,,he's only half way
Dialogue: 0,0:55:39.00,0:55:41.00,Default,,0,0,0,,left.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:41.00,0:55:43.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Even if it's only
Dialogue: 0,0:55:43.00,0:55:45.00,Default,,0,0,0,,one millionth of an inch
Dialogue: 0,0:55:45.00,0:55:47.00,Default,,0,0,0,,he still can't get there.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:47.00,0:55:49.00,Default,,0,0,0,,He still can't get there.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:49.00,0:55:51.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Now I was telling you more
Dialogue: 0,0:55:51.00,0:55:53.00,Default,,0,0,0,,about likelihoods.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:53.00,0:55:55.00,Default,,0,0,0,,The more often you choose
Dialogue: 0,0:55:55.00,0:55:57.00,Default,,0,0,0,,the more likely you choose
Dialogue: 0,0:55:57.00,0:55:59.00,Default,,0,0,0,,a certain choice
Dialogue: 0,0:55:59.00,0:56:01.00,Default,,0,0,0,,with an infinite number of choices
Dialogue: 0,0:56:01.00,0:56:03.00,Default,,0,0,0,,the more likely you are
Dialogue: 0,0:56:03.00,0:56:05.00,Default,,0,0,0,,to choose that again.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:05.00,0:56:07.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Each time you have an infinite possibility.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:07.00,0:56:09.09,Default,,0,0,0,,The fact that you've
Dialogue: 0,0:56:09.09,0:56:11.09,Default,,0,0,0,,chosen this once
Dialogue: 0,0:56:11.09,0:56:13.09,Default,,0,0,0,,and especially if you repeat the choice
Dialogue: 0,0:56:13.09,0:56:15.09,Default,,0,0,0,,quickly, quickly, quickly
Dialogue: 0,0:56:15.09,0:56:17.09,Default,,0,0,0,,the likelihood of your choosing that again
Dialogue: 0,0:56:17.09,0:56:19.09,Default,,0,0,0,,gets higher and higher.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:19.09,0:56:21.09,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a spiritual choice
Dialogue: 0,0:56:21.09,0:56:23.09,Default,,0,0,0,,to forgive, to be
Dialogue: 0,0:56:23.09,0:56:25.09,Default,,0,0,0,,gracious, etc.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:25.09,0:56:27.09,Default,,0,0,0,,The likelihood goes up
Dialogue: 0,0:56:27.09,0:56:29.09,Default,,0,0,0,,that you will choose that again.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:29.09,0:56:31.09,Default,,0,0,0,,So this also reflects intention.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:31.09,0:56:33.13,Default,,0,0,0,,And we spoke of the work
Dialogue: 0,0:56:33.13,0:56:35.13,Default,,0,0,0,,of the doctor
Dialogue: 0,0:56:35.13,0:56:37.13,Default,,0,0,0,,whose name begins with an M
Dialogue: 0,0:56:37.13,0:56:39.19,Default,,0,0,0,,I forget now.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:39.19,0:56:41.90,Default,,0,0,0,,The work on intention.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:41.90,0:56:44.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah?
Dialogue: 0,0:56:44.44,0:56:46.44,Default,,0,0,0,,That intention
Dialogue: 0,0:56:46.44,0:56:48.44,Default,,0,0,0,,then says
Dialogue: 0,0:56:48.44,0:56:50.44,Default,,0,0,0,,so your intention.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:50.44,0:56:52.44,Default,,0,0,0,,You're stating your intention.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:52.44,0:56:54.44,Default,,0,0,0,,That intention now greatly increases
Dialogue: 0,0:56:54.44,0:56:56.44,Default,,0,0,0,,the likelihood
Dialogue: 0,0:56:56.44,0:56:58.44,Default,,0,0,0,,of certain choices.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:58.44,0:57:00.44,Default,,0,0,0,,So this is partly an argument to free will.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:00.44,0:57:02.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Because there is the argument
Dialogue: 0,0:57:02.44,0:57:04.44,Default,,0,0,0,,that there is no such thing as free will.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:04.44,0:57:06.44,Default,,0,0,0,,But it ignores
Dialogue: 0,0:57:06.44,0:57:08.44,Default,,0,0,0,,what we just got through saying.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:08.44,0:57:10.44,Default,,0,0,0,,There is dominance of choice.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:10.44,0:57:12.44,Default,,0,0,0,,So when you make a dominant choice in this direction
Dialogue: 0,0:57:12.44,0:57:14.44,Default,,0,0,0,,then you influence
Dialogue: 0,0:57:14.44,0:57:16.44,Default,,0,0,0,,the whole field.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:16.44,0:57:18.44,Default,,0,0,0,,The likelihood
Dialogue: 0,0:57:18.44,0:57:20.44,Default,,0,0,0,,is much greater that you will choose
Dialogue: 0,0:57:20.44,0:57:22.44,Default,,0,0,0,,a positive option the next time also.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:22.44,0:57:24.67,Default,,0,0,0,,So the holier
Dialogue: 0,0:57:24.67,0:57:26.67,Default,,0,0,0,,you get, the holier you get.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:26.67,0:57:30.03,Default,,0,0,0,,And the worser you get, the worser
Dialogue: 0,0:57:30.03,0:57:32.03,Default,,0,0,0,,you get.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:32.03,0:57:34.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Therefore,
Dialogue: 0,0:57:34.13,0:57:36.13,Default,,0,0,0,,people who are into spiritual integrity
Dialogue: 0,0:57:36.13,0:57:38.13,Default,,0,0,0,,will, yes,
Dialogue: 0,0:57:38.13,0:57:40.13,Default,,0,0,0,,admit a mistake as soon as
Dialogue: 0,0:57:40.13,0:57:42.13,Default,,0,0,0,,they make it and say, I just made a mistake.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:42.13,0:57:44.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Because you
Dialogue: 0,0:57:44.42,0:57:46.42,Default,,0,0,0,,don't want its energy to be out there
Dialogue: 0,0:57:46.42,0:57:48.42,Default,,0,0,0,,and attract other mistakes.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:48.42,0:57:50.42,Default,,0,0,0,,So if you call it by its name
Dialogue: 0,0:57:50.42,0:57:52.42,Default,,0,0,0,,say, you know, that was a mistake
Dialogue: 0,0:57:52.42,0:57:54.42,Default,,0,0,0,,you made a name wrong.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:54.42,0:57:56.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Somebody from history
Dialogue: 0,0:57:56.42,0:57:58.42,Default,,0,0,0,,because
Dialogue: 0,0:57:58.42,0:58:00.42,Default,,0,0,0,,80 year memory is not as great as it was at 30
Dialogue: 0,0:58:00.42,0:58:02.42,Default,,0,0,0,,you know, you can forget a name.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:02.42,0:58:04.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Especially when there is so much
Dialogue: 0,0:58:04.42,0:58:06.42,Default,,0,0,0,,publicity about them, their name gets bandied
Dialogue: 0,0:58:06.42,0:58:08.42,Default,,0,0,0,,about so much that you begin to confuse it
Dialogue: 0,0:58:08.42,0:58:10.42,Default,,0,0,0,,with other people in the same
Dialogue: 0,0:58:10.42,0:58:12.48,Default,,0,0,0,,time era.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:12.48,0:58:14.48,Default,,0,0,0,,So the important thing was to remember
Dialogue: 0,0:58:14.48,0:58:16.48,Default,,0,0,0,,that a double personality can exist.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:16.48,0:58:18.61,Default,,0,0,0,,They do exist.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:18.61,0:58:20.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Their effect on our life
Dialogue: 0,0:58:20.61,0:58:22.65,Default,,0,0,0,,has been devastating.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:22.65,0:58:24.65,Default,,0,0,0,,It is a true clinical condition
Dialogue: 0,0:58:24.65,0:58:26.65,Default,,0,0,0,,and it is a strange
Dialogue: 0,0:58:26.65,0:58:28.65,Default,,0,0,0,,karma. I've never researched
Dialogue: 0,0:58:28.65,0:58:30.65,Default,,0,0,0,,the karma of why there's
Dialogue: 0,0:58:30.65,0:58:32.65,Default,,0,0,0,,two different personalities in one
Dialogue: 0,0:58:32.65,0:58:34.65,Default,,0,0,0,,body. And they trade off
Dialogue: 0,0:58:34.65,0:58:36.65,Default,,0,0,0,,time with each other. They trade off
Dialogue: 0,0:58:36.65,0:58:38.84,Default,,0,0,0,,you've had them for two weeks now
Dialogue: 0,0:58:38.84,0:58:41.13,Default,,0,0,0,,for God's sake.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:41.13,0:58:43.13,Default,,0,0,0,,I haven't even been able to kill anybody for weeks.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:43.13,0:58:45.36,Default,,0,0,0,,And that guy comes on
Dialogue: 0,0:58:45.36,0:58:47.36,Default,,0,0,0,,okay, let's go and have a good time
Dialogue: 0,0:58:47.36,0:58:49.36,Default,,0,0,0,,and stab some people to death.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:49.36,0:58:51.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Stab some children and a nice widow or two.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:51.36,0:58:53.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Pow, pow, pow.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:53.42,0:58:55.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Bang. That one goes out.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:55.61,0:58:57.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Well now this one has to go to jail because of this one.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:57.61,0:58:59.61,Default,,0,0,0,,And of course there's famous criminals.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:59.61,0:59:01.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Famous serial criminals
Dialogue: 0,0:59:01.61,0:59:04.73,Default,,0,0,0,,that are alternate
Dialogue: 0,0:59:04.73,0:59:06.73,Default,,0,0,0,,personalities. You remember the one
Dialogue: 0,0:59:06.73,0:59:08.86,Default,,0,0,0,,that killed Sam
Dialogue: 0,0:59:08.86,0:59:10.86,Default,,0,0,0,,or something like that. God was speaking to him
Dialogue: 0,0:59:10.86,0:59:13.17,Default,,0,0,0,,to kill people.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:13.17,0:59:15.17,Default,,0,0,0,,And the question then
Dialogue: 0,0:59:15.17,0:59:17.17,Default,,0,0,0,,is a judicial one.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:17.17,0:59:19.17,Default,,0,0,0,,You've got to imprison the innocent one
Dialogue: 0,0:59:19.17,0:59:21.17,Default,,0,0,0,,because the criminal
Dialogue: 0,0:59:21.17,0:59:23.46,Default,,0,0,0,,one
Dialogue: 0,0:59:23.46,0:59:25.55,Default,,0,0,0,,is a criminal.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:25.55,0:59:27.55,Default,,0,0,0,,You were going to ask me a question, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:59:27.55,0:59:29.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes. At consciousness
Dialogue: 0,0:59:29.55,0:59:31.55,Default,,0,0,0,,levels below enlightenment
Dialogue: 0,0:59:31.55,0:59:37.11,Default,,0,0,0,,is there a personal me or does it just
Dialogue: 0,0:59:37.11,0:59:39.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, are you asking about the reality of it
Dialogue: 0,0:59:39.11,0:59:41.11,Default,,0,0,0,,or the illusion of it? There
Dialogue: 0,0:59:41.11,0:59:43.11,Default,,0,0,0,,below 200
Dialogue: 0,0:59:43.11,0:59:45.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, there is a
Dialogue: 0,0:59:45.78,0:59:48.36,Default,,0,0,0,,personal me. Yeah, there's a
Dialogue: 0,0:59:48.36,0:59:50.36,Default,,0,0,0,,me. It assumes that
Dialogue: 0,0:59:50.36,0:59:52.36,Default,,0,0,0,,I am the experiencer
Dialogue: 0,0:59:52.36,0:59:54.36,Default,,0,0,0,,primarily. And then
Dialogue: 0,0:59:54.36,0:59:56.36,Default,,0,0,0,,as you get higher you become more aware
Dialogue: 0,0:59:56.36,0:59:58.36,Default,,0,0,0,,that you're the
Dialogue: 0,0:59:58.36,1:00:00.36,Default,,0,0,0,,field which
Dialogue: 0,1:00:00.36,1:00:02.36,Default,,0,0,0,,is able to identify that.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:02.36,1:00:04.36,Default,,0,0,0,,So the below
Dialogue: 0,1:00:04.36,1:00:06.36,Default,,0,0,0,,200 people exist but they don't
Dialogue: 0,1:00:06.36,1:00:08.55,Default,,0,0,0,,really comprehend the
Dialogue: 0,1:00:08.55,1:00:10.55,Default,,0,0,0,,significance of existence. People say
Dialogue: 0,1:00:10.55,1:00:12.90,Default,,0,0,0,,how can that be? Well
Dialogue: 0,1:00:12.90,1:00:14.90,Default,,0,0,0,,if you comprehended the value of existence
Dialogue: 0,1:00:14.90,1:00:16.90,Default,,0,0,0,,you wouldn't be able to kill anybody.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:16.90,1:00:18.90,Default,,0,0,0,,It's only when they no longer are
Dialogue: 0,1:00:18.90,1:00:20.90,Default,,0,0,0,,real to you that you can kill them.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:20.90,1:00:23.28,Default,,0,0,0,,So below
Dialogue: 0,1:00:23.28,1:00:25.28,Default,,0,0,0,,200 people are dangerous because
Dialogue: 0,1:00:25.28,1:00:27.28,Default,,0,0,0,,they do not value your
Dialogue: 0,1:00:27.28,1:00:29.67,Default,,0,0,0,,life. They do not
Dialogue: 0,1:00:29.67,1:00:31.67,Default,,0,0,0,,value your life. They can blow up a whole
Dialogue: 0,1:00:31.67,1:00:34.28,Default,,0,0,0,,busload of children.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:34.28,1:00:37.71,Default,,0,0,0,,And they don't feel bad about it.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:37.71,1:00:39.71,Default,,0,0,0,,They themselves don't experience the
Dialogue: 0,1:00:39.71,1:00:41.71,Default,,0,0,0,,value of their own
Dialogue: 0,1:00:41.71,1:00:43.71,Default,,0,0,0,,life as a divine gift. Therefore
Dialogue: 0,1:00:43.71,1:00:45.71,Default,,0,0,0,,they don't value it in others.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:45.71,1:00:47.76,Default,,0,0,0,,So if you don't value your own money
Dialogue: 0,1:00:47.76,1:00:49.76,Default,,0,0,0,,you don't value other people's money either.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:49.76,1:00:52.71,Default,,0,0,0,,So
Dialogue: 0,1:00:52.71,1:00:54.71,Default,,0,0,0,,it sounds strange to say that people below
Dialogue: 0,1:00:54.71,1:00:56.71,Default,,0,0,0,,200 are not aware that they
Dialogue: 0,1:00:56.71,1:00:58.71,Default,,0,0,0,,exist. But I'm telling you about the word
Dialogue: 0,1:00:58.71,1:01:00.71,Default,,0,0,0,,awareness. They exist but they're not really
Dialogue: 0,1:01:00.71,1:01:02.71,Default,,0,0,0,,aware that they exist as such.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:02.71,1:01:04.71,Default,,0,0,0,,And above 200 but
Dialogue: 0,1:01:04.71,1:01:06.88,Default,,0,0,0,,still below enlightenment, is there a personal
Dialogue: 0,1:01:06.88,1:01:09.38,Default,,0,0,0,,me? Oh there very definitely is a
Dialogue: 0,1:01:09.38,1:01:11.38,Default,,0,0,0,,personal operation of a personal me.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:11.38,1:01:13.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Operation is very much
Dialogue: 0,1:01:13.48,1:01:15.48,Default,,0,0,0,,a very personal me. And we spend all
Dialogue: 0,1:01:15.48,1:01:17.48,Default,,0,0,0,,our time worrying about it actually.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:17.48,1:01:19.48,Default,,0,0,0,,The personal me
Dialogue: 0,1:01:19.48,1:01:21.48,Default,,0,0,0,,until you begin to transcend it
Dialogue: 0,1:01:21.48,1:01:23.48,Default,,0,0,0,,and see that it's autonomous.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:23.48,1:01:25.48,Default,,0,0,0,,You get to see the things that are happening
Dialogue: 0,1:01:25.48,1:01:27.48,Default,,0,0,0,,autonomously. However
Dialogue: 0,1:01:27.48,1:01:29.48,Default,,0,0,0,,the autonomous choices
Dialogue: 0,1:01:29.48,1:01:31.48,Default,,0,0,0,,are a consequence of that with
Dialogue: 0,1:01:31.48,1:01:33.48,Default,,0,0,0,,which you have aligned. So
Dialogue: 0,1:01:33.48,1:01:35.48,Default,,0,0,0,,as you choose a higher and higher
Dialogue: 0,1:01:35.48,1:01:37.48,Default,,0,0,0,,commitment even though
Dialogue: 0,1:01:37.48,1:01:39.48,Default,,0,0,0,,they're spontaneous as Medina's
Dialogue: 0,1:01:39.48,1:01:41.48,Default,,0,0,0,,research shows
Dialogue: 0,1:01:41.48,1:01:43.48,Default,,0,0,0,,the choices now begin
Dialogue: 0,1:01:43.48,1:01:45.48,Default,,0,0,0,,to show a preference for that
Dialogue: 0,1:01:45.48,1:01:47.48,Default,,0,0,0,,which is benign and harmless and aligned
Dialogue: 0,1:01:47.48,1:01:49.48,Default,,0,0,0,,with truth rather than
Dialogue: 0,1:01:49.48,1:01:51.80,Default,,0,0,0,,the other way.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:51.80,1:01:53.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Attention set. So Medina calls
Dialogue: 0,1:01:53.80,1:01:55.92,Default,,0,0,0,,it attention set.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:55.92,1:01:57.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Attention set.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:57.92,1:02:00.51,Default,,0,0,0,,So you have
Dialogue: 0,1:02:00.51,1:02:02.51,Default,,0,0,0,,intention and attention
Dialogue: 0,1:02:02.51,1:02:04.51,Default,,0,0,0,,set.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:04.51,1:02:06.57,Default,,0,0,0,,And these tend to dominate it.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:06.57,1:02:08.57,Default,,0,0,0,,These are dominant fields
Dialogue: 0,1:02:08.57,1:02:10.57,Default,,0,0,0,,of consciousness.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:10.57,1:02:12.57,Default,,0,0,0,,So you might picture fields
Dialogue: 0,1:02:12.57,1:02:14.59,Default,,0,0,0,,of progressive power.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:14.59,1:02:16.59,Default,,0,0,0,,And the smaller little
Dialogue: 0,1:02:16.59,1:02:18.59,Default,,0,0,0,,fields like the weather down here
Dialogue: 0,1:02:18.59,1:02:20.59,Default,,0,0,0,,is being dominated by
Dialogue: 0,1:02:20.59,1:02:22.59,Default,,0,0,0,,a more powerful weather field
Dialogue: 0,1:02:22.59,1:02:24.59,Default,,0,0,0,,which is dominated by an even higher
Dialogue: 0,1:02:24.59,1:02:26.59,Default,,0,0,0,,weather field. So
Dialogue: 0,1:02:26.59,1:02:30.01,Default,,0,0,0,,by commitment then
Dialogue: 0,1:02:30.01,1:02:32.01,Default,,0,0,0,,what you're doing is you're setting
Dialogue: 0,1:02:32.01,1:02:34.01,Default,,0,0,0,,the predominant overall field
Dialogue: 0,1:02:34.01,1:02:36.01,Default,,0,0,0,,and out of which
Dialogue: 0,1:02:36.01,1:02:38.01,Default,,0,0,0,,lesser and lesser choices are being made.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:38.01,1:02:40.30,Default,,0,0,0,,So there's still
Dialogue: 0,1:02:40.30,1:02:42.30,Default,,0,0,0,,freedom of the will but it is only
Dialogue: 0,1:02:42.30,1:02:44.30,Default,,0,0,0,,within certain fields.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:44.30,1:02:46.30,Default,,0,0,0,,So
Dialogue: 0,1:02:46.30,1:02:48.30,Default,,0,0,0,,consciousness really has
Dialogue: 0,1:02:48.30,1:02:50.30,Default,,0,0,0,,to do with energy fields.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:50.30,1:02:52.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Energy fields of increasing
Dialogue: 0,1:02:52.40,1:02:54.65,Default,,0,0,0,,power and dominance.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:54.65,1:02:56.65,Default,,0,0,0,,So your spiritual self eventually
Dialogue: 0,1:02:56.65,1:02:58.65,Default,,0,0,0,,becomes the most powerful aspect
Dialogue: 0,1:02:58.65,1:03:00.65,Default,,0,0,0,,as you go over 200.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:00.65,1:03:02.71,Default,,0,0,0,,The etheric
Dialogue: 0,1:03:02.71,1:03:04.71,Default,,0,0,0,,body forms, the etheric brain forms,
Dialogue: 0,1:03:04.71,1:03:06.71,Default,,0,0,0,,you develop
Dialogue: 0,1:03:06.71,1:03:08.71,Default,,0,0,0,,a personal karma
Dialogue: 0,1:03:08.71,1:03:10.71,Default,,0,0,0,,and kundalini
Dialogue: 0,1:03:10.71,1:03:12.71,Default,,0,0,0,,energy dominates
Dialogue: 0,1:03:12.71,1:03:14.71,Default,,0,0,0,,how your brain functions.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:14.71,1:03:16.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Your brain begins
Dialogue: 0,1:03:16.84,1:03:18.84,Default,,0,0,0,,releasing endorphins.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:18.84,1:03:21.00,Default,,0,0,0,,These endorphins
Dialogue: 0,1:03:21.00,1:03:23.00,Default,,0,0,0,,instead of adrenaline.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:23.00,1:03:25.00,Default,,0,0,0,,And the endorphins give you
Dialogue: 0,1:03:25.00,1:03:27.00,Default,,0,0,0,,a right brain
Dialogue: 0,1:03:27.00,1:03:29.00,Default,,0,0,0,,and the brain
Dialogue: 0,1:03:29.00,1:03:31.00,Default,,0,0,0,,dominated by endorphins sees
Dialogue: 0,1:03:31.00,1:03:33.00,Default,,0,0,0,,life as pretty much benign.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:33.00,1:03:35.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Sees life as relatively
Dialogue: 0,1:03:35.00,1:03:37.19,Default,,0,0,0,,benign.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:37.19,1:03:39.19,Default,,0,0,0,,With the proviso as I said
Dialogue: 0,1:03:39.19,1:03:41.19,Default,,0,0,0,,of not being the fool.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:41.19,1:03:43.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Simultaneously not playing the fool.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:45.76,1:03:47.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh aren't they nice?
Dialogue: 0,1:03:49.76,1:03:51.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Who just said that just left the world.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:53.76,1:03:55.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Aren't they nice? It's just a nice doggy.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:55.76,1:03:57.76,Default,,0,0,0,,No that is a tiger.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:57.76,1:03:59.76,Default,,0,0,0,,And he will eat you up.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:59.76,1:04:01.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Not because he hates you but because
Dialogue: 0,1:04:01.76,1:04:03.76,Default,,0,0,0,,he's hungry. Oh I see.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:03.76,1:04:05.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Tigers are not evil.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:05.76,1:04:07.76,Default,,0,0,0,,They just want you for dinner.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:07.76,1:04:10.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Should be a compliment.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:10.38,1:04:12.38,Default,,0,0,0,,He says
Dialogue: 0,1:04:12.38,1:04:14.38,Default,,0,0,0,,I want you for dinner baby.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:18.98,1:04:20.98,Default,,0,0,0,,So that gets you off good and evil
Dialogue: 0,1:04:20.98,1:04:22.98,Default,,0,0,0,,when you see that each thing is only being
Dialogue: 0,1:04:22.98,1:04:24.98,Default,,0,0,0,,what it's able to be
Dialogue: 0,1:04:24.98,1:04:27.11,Default,,0,0,0,,at any point in time.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:27.11,1:04:29.11,Default,,0,0,0,,If it could be different than it is
Dialogue: 0,1:04:29.11,1:04:31.11,Default,,0,0,0,,it would be. Therefore we can't
Dialogue: 0,1:04:31.11,1:04:33.11,Default,,0,0,0,,condemn anybody or anything for being
Dialogue: 0,1:04:33.11,1:04:35.11,Default,,0,0,0,,what they are. So
Dialogue: 0,1:04:35.11,1:04:37.11,Default,,0,0,0,,when I say beware of something
Dialogue: 0,1:04:37.11,1:04:39.11,Default,,0,0,0,,I mean
Dialogue: 0,1:04:39.11,1:04:41.11,Default,,0,0,0,,to beware of its upside and its downside.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:41.11,1:04:43.11,Default,,0,0,0,,It doesn't make it good
Dialogue: 0,1:04:43.11,1:04:45.11,Default,,0,0,0,,or better or bad.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:45.11,1:04:47.11,Default,,0,0,0,,It's just that you see it for what it is.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:47.11,1:04:49.11,Default,,0,0,0,,So I can't say
Dialogue: 0,1:04:49.11,1:04:51.11,Default,,0,0,0,,a Komodo dragon is bad.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:51.11,1:04:53.11,Default,,0,0,0,,There's nothing bad about him.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:53.11,1:04:57.09,Default,,0,0,0,,He just likes to bite people.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:00.32,1:05:02.38,Default,,0,0,0,,That's what it is to be a
Dialogue: 0,1:05:02.38,1:05:04.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Komodo dragon. Yes?
Dialogue: 0,1:05:04.44,1:05:06.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah. Then at a certain level
Dialogue: 0,1:05:06.44,1:05:08.44,Default,,0,0,0,,of consciousness you don't have to come back
Dialogue: 0,1:05:08.44,1:05:10.44,Default,,0,0,0,,as a Komodo dragon.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:10.44,1:05:12.44,Default,,0,0,0,,That's how you evolve from being a Komodo dragon.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:14.44,1:05:16.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes. Who's next?
Dialogue: 0,1:05:16.44,1:05:20.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes. I forgot.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:20.07,1:05:36.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes. Yes.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:36.69,1:05:44.96,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't hear the question.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:44.96,1:05:47.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Dominant. Yes.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:47.76,1:05:49.76,Default,,0,0,0,,It becomes progressively
Dialogue: 0,1:05:49.76,1:05:51.76,Default,,0,0,0,,dominant as you
Dialogue: 0,1:05:51.76,1:05:53.76,Default,,0,0,0,,become aligned with the desire to reach
Dialogue: 0,1:05:53.76,1:05:55.76,Default,,0,0,0,,the truth. The capacity
Dialogue: 0,1:05:55.76,1:05:57.76,Default,,0,0,0,,to discern perception from
Dialogue: 0,1:05:57.76,1:05:59.80,Default,,0,0,0,,essence does not really
Dialogue: 0,1:05:59.80,1:06:01.80,Default,,0,0,0,,manifest until about
Dialogue: 0,1:06:01.80,1:06:03.80,Default,,0,0,0,,consciousness level 300.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:03.80,1:06:05.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Which is the opening
Dialogue: 0,1:06:05.80,1:06:07.80,Default,,0,0,0,,of the third eye of the Buddhic body.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:07.80,1:06:09.80,Default,,0,0,0,,The third eye of the etheric Buddhic body.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:09.80,1:06:11.80,Default,,0,0,0,,One of the higher bodies.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:11.80,1:06:14.00,Default,,0,0,0,,And when the
Dialogue: 0,1:06:14.00,1:06:16.00,Default,,0,0,0,,opening of the third eye
Dialogue: 0,1:06:16.00,1:06:18.00,Default,,0,0,0,,is called discernment.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:18.00,1:06:20.00,Default,,0,0,0,,So discernment is not really
Dialogue: 0,1:06:20.00,1:06:22.00,Default,,0,0,0,,dominant
Dialogue: 0,1:06:22.00,1:06:24.00,Default,,0,0,0,,until consciousness level
Dialogue: 0,1:06:24.00,1:06:26.67,Default,,0,0,0,,600.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:26.67,1:06:28.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Up to that time
Dialogue: 0,1:06:28.69,1:06:31.98,Default,,0,0,0,,one can be deceived quite easily.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:31.98,1:06:33.98,Default,,0,0,0,,At 600
Dialogue: 0,1:06:33.98,1:06:35.98,Default,,0,0,0,,you sense
Dialogue: 0,1:06:35.98,1:06:38.80,Default,,0,0,0,,the wolf in the sheep's clothing.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:38.80,1:06:40.80,Default,,0,0,0,,And like with
Dialogue: 0,1:06:40.80,1:06:42.80,Default,,0,0,0,,calibration I sense something out.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:42.80,1:06:44.88,Default,,0,0,0,,And then I calibrate
Dialogue: 0,1:06:44.88,1:06:46.88,Default,,0,0,0,,it and I say yes I got
Dialogue: 0,1:06:46.88,1:06:48.88,Default,,0,0,0,,what the second personality is now.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:48.88,1:06:50.88,Default,,0,0,0,,But you begin
Dialogue: 0,1:06:50.88,1:06:52.88,Default,,0,0,0,,to sense it.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:52.88,1:06:55.03,Default,,0,0,0,,So that's at
Dialogue: 0,1:06:55.03,1:06:57.03,Default,,0,0,0,,600. 600 is
Dialogue: 0,1:06:57.03,1:06:59.03,Default,,0,0,0,,the first level of true
Dialogue: 0,1:06:59.03,1:07:01.03,Default,,0,0,0,,enlightenment.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:01.03,1:07:03.03,Default,,0,0,0,,570 is saintliness.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:03.03,1:07:05.03,Default,,0,0,0,,580, 590 is joy.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:05.03,1:07:07.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Ecstasy.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:07.03,1:07:09.32,Default,,0,0,0,,And finally at 600
Dialogue: 0,1:07:09.32,1:07:11.32,Default,,0,0,0,,there is an incredible
Dialogue: 0,1:07:11.32,1:07:13.67,Default,,0,0,0,,calm. There is
Dialogue: 0,1:07:13.67,1:07:15.67,Default,,0,0,0,,experientially the
Dialogue: 0,1:07:15.67,1:07:17.90,Default,,0,0,0,,peace of God.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:17.90,1:07:19.90,Default,,0,0,0,,And one doesn't really have to remain here
Dialogue: 0,1:07:19.90,1:07:21.90,Default,,0,0,0,,any further.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:21.90,1:07:23.90,Default,,0,0,0,,At 600 you have permission to leave.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:23.90,1:07:26.28,Default,,0,0,0,,And it's a state of
Dialogue: 0,1:07:26.28,1:07:28.69,Default,,0,0,0,,infinite peace.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:28.69,1:07:30.69,Default,,0,0,0,,And infinite oneness beyond
Dialogue: 0,1:07:30.69,1:07:32.82,Default,,0,0,0,,all description.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:32.82,1:07:34.82,Default,,0,0,0,,The peace of God beyond all understanding.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:34.82,1:07:36.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Which is what you hear in
Dialogue: 0,1:07:36.82,1:07:38.82,Default,,0,0,0,,church and sermons. The peace of God
Dialogue: 0,1:07:38.82,1:07:40.82,Default,,0,0,0,,beyond all understanding.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:40.82,1:07:42.82,Default,,0,0,0,,It emerges at level 600.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:42.82,1:07:44.82,Default,,0,0,0,,As I say at that level
Dialogue: 0,1:07:44.82,1:07:47.23,Default,,0,0,0,,you can leave. And 50%
Dialogue: 0,1:07:47.23,1:07:49.23,Default,,0,0,0,,of people who reach that level do leave.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:49.23,1:07:51.53,Default,,0,0,0,,You're invited to leave.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:51.53,1:07:53.53,Default,,0,0,0,,As I say it's almost invitational
Dialogue: 0,1:07:53.53,1:07:55.78,Default,,0,0,0,,to
Dialogue: 0,1:07:55.78,1:07:57.78,Default,,0,0,0,,do so. And then for reasons
Dialogue: 0,1:07:57.78,1:07:59.82,Default,,0,0,0,,remembered
Dialogue: 0,1:07:59.82,1:08:01.82,Default,,0,0,0,,or not
Dialogue: 0,1:08:01.82,1:08:03.82,Default,,0,0,0,,remembered
Dialogue: 0,1:08:03.82,1:08:05.82,Default,,0,0,0,,the choice is made.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:05.82,1:08:07.82,Default,,0,0,0,,But again one is sort of
Dialogue: 0,1:08:07.82,1:08:09.82,Default,,0,0,0,,the witness to the choice. So when it
Dialogue: 0,1:08:09.82,1:08:11.82,Default,,0,0,0,,happens one doesn't
Dialogue: 0,1:08:11.82,1:08:13.82,Default,,0,0,0,,know whether they're going to walk on or not
Dialogue: 0,1:08:13.82,1:08:16.30,Default,,0,0,0,,walk on. And it's not really
Dialogue: 0,1:08:16.30,1:08:18.30,Default,,0,0,0,,your problem. There isn't any of you
Dialogue: 0,1:08:18.30,1:08:20.30,Default,,0,0,0,,left to worry about it. So no choice
Dialogue: 0,1:08:20.30,1:08:22.30,Default,,0,0,0,,has to be made. It seems
Dialogue: 0,1:08:22.30,1:08:24.61,Default,,0,0,0,,to be a karmic propensity.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:24.61,1:08:26.61,Default,,0,0,0,,And my own condition
Dialogue: 0,1:08:26.61,1:08:28.61,Default,,0,0,0,,I sort of intuited
Dialogue: 0,1:08:28.61,1:08:30.61,Default,,0,0,0,,had to do with an agreement.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:30.61,1:08:32.61,Default,,0,0,0,,With the fulfillment of an
Dialogue: 0,1:08:32.61,1:08:34.61,Default,,0,0,0,,agreement prior
Dialogue: 0,1:08:34.61,1:08:36.61,Default,,0,0,0,,to this incarnation. And I witnessed
Dialogue: 0,1:08:36.61,1:08:38.61,Default,,0,0,0,,the agreement
Dialogue: 0,1:08:38.61,1:08:40.61,Default,,0,0,0,,taking place. You know.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:40.61,1:08:42.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Like an agreement
Dialogue: 0,1:08:42.61,1:08:44.61,Default,,0,0,0,,that you agreed to fulfill.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:44.61,1:08:47.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Some people
Dialogue: 0,1:08:47.55,1:08:50.02,Default,,0,0,0,,may not be aware that
Dialogue: 0,1:08:50.02,1:08:52.02,Default,,0,0,0,,such a thing goes on in their life. But I think
Dialogue: 0,1:08:52.02,1:08:54.09,Default,,0,0,0,,all of us have made agreements
Dialogue: 0,1:08:54.09,1:08:56.09,Default,,0,0,0,,and promises and that these
Dialogue: 0,1:08:56.09,1:08:58.09,Default,,0,0,0,,are playing a part in our life
Dialogue: 0,1:08:58.09,1:09:00.09,Default,,0,0,0,,right now. Everybody
Dialogue: 0,1:09:00.09,1:09:02.09,Default,,0,0,0,,here has obviously made a
Dialogue: 0,1:09:02.09,1:09:04.09,Default,,0,0,0,,spiritual agreement, commitment or declaration
Dialogue: 0,1:09:04.09,1:09:06.09,Default,,0,0,0,,or they wouldn't be here.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:06.09,1:09:08.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Because this is not a class on bull fighting.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:10.09,1:09:12.09,Default,,0,0,0,,How to gore a bull.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:12.09,1:09:14.09,Default,,0,0,0,,So obviously
Dialogue: 0,1:09:14.09,1:09:16.09,Default,,0,0,0,,everyone here has made one.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:16.09,1:09:18.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Some don't consciously
Dialogue: 0,1:09:18.09,1:09:20.09,Default,,0,0,0,,remember it in this lifetime.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:20.09,1:09:22.09,Default,,0,0,0,,But to be attracted to such a group
Dialogue: 0,1:09:22.09,1:09:24.09,Default,,0,0,0,,and a group that calibrates as high as this
Dialogue: 0,1:09:24.09,1:09:26.09,Default,,0,0,0,,one has to have made such a commitment.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:26.09,1:09:28.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:28.18,1:09:32.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:32.68,1:09:39.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes. No.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:39.52,1:09:41.52,Default,,0,0,0,,You don't identify a witness observer.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:41.52,1:09:43.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Well yes you do.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:43.52,1:09:45.52,Default,,0,0,0,,At first you realize that
Dialogue: 0,1:09:45.52,1:09:47.71,Default,,0,0,0,,there's
Dialogue: 0,1:09:47.71,1:09:49.71,Default,,0,0,0,,the witnessing and the observing.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:49.71,1:09:51.71,Default,,0,0,0,,And you observe them as phenomena
Dialogue: 0,1:09:51.71,1:09:53.71,Default,,0,0,0,,not as a personage.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:53.71,1:09:55.71,Default,,0,0,0,,There's no watcher and no witness
Dialogue: 0,1:09:55.71,1:09:57.71,Default,,0,0,0,,as an entity.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:57.71,1:09:59.71,Default,,0,0,0,,There's only these functions.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:59.71,1:10:01.71,Default,,0,0,0,,You'll notice that witnessing and watching
Dialogue: 0,1:10:01.71,1:10:03.71,Default,,0,0,0,,are going on all the time.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:03.71,1:10:05.73,Default,,0,0,0,,And these go on
Dialogue: 0,1:10:05.73,1:10:07.73,Default,,0,0,0,,independently of your
Dialogue: 0,1:10:07.73,1:10:09.73,Default,,0,0,0,,you don't have any say so
Dialogue: 0,1:10:09.73,1:10:11.73,Default,,0,0,0,,about it. In other words it's an aspect
Dialogue: 0,1:10:11.73,1:10:14.09,Default,,0,0,0,,of consciousness itself.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:14.09,1:10:16.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Unless you were witnessing and watching
Dialogue: 0,1:10:16.09,1:10:18.09,Default,,0,0,0,,you wouldn't know how to respond to the world.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:18.09,1:10:20.09,Default,,0,0,0,,So the witnessing and the watching
Dialogue: 0,1:10:20.09,1:10:22.09,Default,,0,0,0,,are automatic phenomena.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:22.09,1:10:24.09,Default,,0,0,0,,And therefore
Dialogue: 0,1:10:24.09,1:10:26.09,Default,,0,0,0,,the farther you get back
Dialogue: 0,1:10:26.09,1:10:28.09,Default,,0,0,0,,to the observer and then the witness
Dialogue: 0,1:10:28.09,1:10:30.09,Default,,0,0,0,,and then finally
Dialogue: 0,1:10:30.09,1:10:32.09,Default,,0,0,0,,what is it that's witnessing and observing
Dialogue: 0,1:10:32.09,1:10:34.09,Default,,0,0,0,,brings you back to conscious awareness.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:34.09,1:10:36.09,Default,,0,0,0,,You realize
Dialogue: 0,1:10:36.09,1:10:38.09,Default,,0,0,0,,that what's going on is awareness
Dialogue: 0,1:10:38.09,1:10:40.09,Default,,0,0,0,,of these phenomena.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:40.09,1:10:42.09,Default,,0,0,0,,What's closer to your reality
Dialogue: 0,1:10:42.09,1:10:44.09,Default,,0,0,0,,is the awareness itself.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:44.09,1:10:46.09,Default,,0,0,0,,That your inner reality
Dialogue: 0,1:10:46.09,1:10:48.15,Default,,0,0,0,,is the awareness
Dialogue: 0,1:10:48.15,1:10:54.76,Default,,0,0,0,,quality of consciousness.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:54.76,1:10:56.76,Default,,0,0,0,,No, because there's still
Dialogue: 0,1:10:56.76,1:10:58.76,Default,,0,0,0,,an illusion beyond that.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:58.76,1:11:01.94,Default,,0,0,0,,The illusion has to do with
Dialogue: 0,1:11:01.94,1:11:05.13,Default,,0,0,0,,let's see
Dialogue: 0,1:11:05.13,1:11:07.68,Default,,0,0,0,,that there is someone
Dialogue: 0,1:11:07.68,1:11:09.68,Default,,0,0,0,,that has
Dialogue: 0,1:11:09.68,1:11:11.68,Default,,0,0,0,,it has to do with the life itself
Dialogue: 0,1:11:11.68,1:11:13.89,Default,,0,0,0,,that one identifies
Dialogue: 0,1:11:13.89,1:11:15.89,Default,,0,0,0,,these phenomena
Dialogue: 0,1:11:15.89,1:11:18.11,Default,,0,0,0,,as life.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:18.11,1:11:20.11,Default,,0,0,0,,And
Dialogue: 0,1:11:20.11,1:11:23.52,Default,,0,0,0,,the last story I can remember
Dialogue: 0,1:11:23.52,1:11:25.52,Default,,0,0,0,,had to do with relinquishing
Dialogue: 0,1:11:27.81,1:11:30.72,Default,,0,0,0,,the desire
Dialogue: 0,1:11:30.72,1:11:34.85,Default,,0,0,0,,to be.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:34.85,1:11:36.98,Default,,0,0,0,,The desire to be
Dialogue: 0,1:11:36.98,1:11:38.98,Default,,0,0,0,,was somehow associated with life itself.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:38.98,1:11:41.39,Default,,0,0,0,,That if one gave up
Dialogue: 0,1:11:41.39,1:11:43.39,Default,,0,0,0,,life one would no longer be.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:43.39,1:11:45.39,Default,,0,0,0,,So the block was
Dialogue: 0,1:11:45.39,1:11:47.65,Default,,0,0,0,,to surrender the source
Dialogue: 0,1:11:47.65,1:11:49.65,Default,,0,0,0,,of life itself to divinity.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:49.65,1:11:51.85,Default,,0,0,0,,The only thing left
Dialogue: 0,1:11:51.85,1:11:55.28,Default,,0,0,0,,was the
Dialogue: 0,1:11:55.28,1:11:57.28,Default,,0,0,0,,thought that I exist
Dialogue: 0,1:11:57.28,1:11:59.77,Default,,0,0,0,,and I exist because of
Dialogue: 0,1:11:59.77,1:12:01.77,Default,,0,0,0,,life. And the source of life
Dialogue: 0,1:12:01.77,1:12:05.18,Default,,0,0,0,,so just as I had
Dialogue: 0,1:12:05.18,1:12:07.18,Default,,0,0,0,,laid down ecstasy
Dialogue: 0,1:12:07.18,1:12:09.18,Default,,0,0,0,,joy
Dialogue: 0,1:12:09.18,1:12:11.18,Default,,0,0,0,,and each thing as it arose
Dialogue: 0,1:12:11.18,1:12:13.27,Default,,0,0,0,,there was nothing left
Dialogue: 0,1:12:13.27,1:12:15.27,Default,,0,0,0,,with which I
Dialogue: 0,1:12:15.27,1:12:17.27,Default,,0,0,0,,identified except life itself.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:17.27,1:12:19.47,Default,,0,0,0,,And therefore
Dialogue: 0,1:12:19.47,1:12:21.92,Default,,0,0,0,,there was a knowingness
Dialogue: 0,1:12:21.92,1:12:23.92,Default,,0,0,0,,this too oh lord
Dialogue: 0,1:12:23.92,1:12:25.92,Default,,0,0,0,,do I surrender to thee.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:25.92,1:12:27.94,Default,,0,0,0,,And I surrendered life itself
Dialogue: 0,1:12:27.94,1:12:29.94,Default,,0,0,0,,and then
Dialogue: 0,1:12:29.94,1:12:31.94,Default,,0,0,0,,went through actual experience
Dialogue: 0,1:12:31.94,1:12:33.94,Default,,0,0,0,,of death and it was agony.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:33.94,1:12:36.14,Default,,0,0,0,,It was agony but the
Dialogue: 0,1:12:36.14,1:12:38.59,Default,,0,0,0,,agony was only
Dialogue: 0,1:12:38.59,1:12:40.59,Default,,0,0,0,,for moments.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:40.59,1:12:42.59,Default,,0,0,0,,One actually feels one's self
Dialogue: 0,1:12:42.59,1:12:44.59,Default,,0,0,0,,with a small s
Dialogue: 0,1:12:44.59,1:12:46.88,Default,,0,0,0,,actually die.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:46.88,1:12:48.88,Default,,0,0,0,,It actually dies.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:48.88,1:12:50.88,Default,,0,0,0,,And you experience the death agony.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:50.88,1:12:53.31,Default,,0,0,0,,And beyond that the door opens
Dialogue: 0,1:12:53.31,1:12:57.78,Default,,0,0,0,,and excels his deal.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:57.78,1:12:59.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Glory to God shines forth
Dialogue: 0,1:12:59.78,1:13:01.78,Default,,0,0,0,,is all the radiance of all existence.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:01.78,1:13:04.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Then you're beyond
Dialogue: 0,1:13:04.30,1:13:06.30,Default,,0,0,0,,all of that.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:06.30,1:13:09.44,Default,,0,0,0,,What did we do at 3 o'clock?
Dialogue: 0,1:13:09.44,1:13:12.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh
Dialogue: 0,1:13:12.06,1:13:14.06,Default,,0,0,0,,I thought I had some spiritual duty to perform
Dialogue: 0,1:13:14.06,1:13:19.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Take a quick break.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:19.28,1:13:23.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Take a quick break.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:23.18,1:13:27.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Take a quick break.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:27.96,1:13:32.01,Default,,0,0,0,,God bless you all.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:32.01,1:13:34.01,Default,,0,0,0,,We'd like to say thank you for everything.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:34.01,1:13:36.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:36.01,1:13:38.01,Default,,0,0,0,,And we should say hi from Cornelia from Germany.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:38.01,1:13:40.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh yes.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:40.01,1:13:42.01,Default,,0,0,0,,She's doing the Cologne seminar.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:42.01,1:13:45.80,Default,,0,0,0,,She's very excited.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:45.80,1:13:48.89,Default,,0,0,0,,That's very nice. Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:48.89,1:13:50.89,Default,,0,0,0,,And maybe you can talk about
Dialogue: 0,1:13:50.89,1:13:53.43,Default,,0,0,0,,transcending the attachment to personal love.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:53.43,1:13:56.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Attachment to personal love.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:56.68,1:13:58.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:58.68,1:14:00.75,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a statuation
Dialogue: 0,1:14:00.75,1:14:02.75,Default,,0,0,0,,run by your endocrine system hormone.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:02.75,1:14:05.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:05.84,1:14:08.00,Default,,0,0,0,,There's a craving.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:08.00,1:14:10.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Cravingness.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:10.53,1:14:14.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Cravingness is coming out of your animal.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:14.10,1:14:16.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Try to replace the cravingness
Dialogue: 0,1:14:16.10,1:14:18.10,Default,,0,0,0,,with a lovingness.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:18.10,1:14:20.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Because cravingness is
Dialogue: 0,1:14:20.10,1:14:22.23,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm deficient and I need to get.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:22.23,1:14:24.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Lovingness is
Dialogue: 0,1:14:24.23,1:14:26.93,Default,,0,0,0,,you complete my
Dialogue: 0,1:14:26.93,1:14:28.93,Default,,0,0,0,,fulfill my
Dialogue: 0,1:14:28.93,1:14:30.97,Default,,0,0,0,,happiness.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:30.97,1:14:33.86,Default,,0,0,0,,So one is I have to have
Dialogue: 0,1:14:33.86,1:14:35.86,Default,,0,0,0,,it's coming from one's
Dialogue: 0,1:14:35.86,1:14:37.86,Default,,0,0,0,,animal instinctual nature.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:37.86,1:14:40.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Hippopotamuses do it.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:40.69,1:14:42.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Elephants do it.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:42.69,1:14:44.69,Default,,0,0,0,,So you've got to do it.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:49.76,1:14:51.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Being a young male is not an enviable
Dialogue: 0,1:14:51.76,1:14:53.81,Default,,0,0,0,,place in life frankly.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:57.81,1:15:01.57,Default,,0,0,0,,To transcend it requires
Dialogue: 0,1:15:01.57,1:15:04.00,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll tell you how to
Dialogue: 0,1:15:04.00,1:15:06.00,Default,,0,0,0,,transcend it. How to transcend any
Dialogue: 0,1:15:06.00,1:15:08.00,Default,,0,0,0,,desire of a physical nature
Dialogue: 0,1:15:08.00,1:15:10.35,Default,,0,0,0,,How to overcome a craving.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:10.35,1:15:12.38,Default,,0,0,0,,A craving
Dialogue: 0,1:15:12.38,1:15:14.38,Default,,0,0,0,,first starts in your mind
Dialogue: 0,1:15:14.38,1:15:16.38,Default,,0,0,0,,as an image.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:16.38,1:15:19.07,Default,,0,0,0,,If you watch this carefully
Dialogue: 0,1:15:19.07,1:15:21.07,Default,,0,0,0,,you'll see any craving
Dialogue: 0,1:15:21.07,1:15:23.07,Default,,0,0,0,,first appears as an image.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:23.07,1:15:25.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Whether it's a cheeseburger or a hamburger
Dialogue: 0,1:15:25.07,1:15:27.18,Default,,0,0,0,,the naked body of the opposite sex
Dialogue: 0,1:15:27.18,1:15:29.18,Default,,0,0,0,,or if you're an alcoholic a drinker.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:29.18,1:15:31.52,Default,,0,0,0,,First comes the image of the drink
Dialogue: 0,1:15:31.52,1:15:33.52,Default,,0,0,0,,and if you don't eliminate it instantly
Dialogue: 0,1:15:33.52,1:15:35.52,Default,,0,0,0,,it draws energy to it.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:35.52,1:15:37.63,Default,,0,0,0,,So when it first appears
Dialogue: 0,1:15:37.63,1:15:39.63,Default,,0,0,0,,it's only about five watts.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:39.63,1:15:41.63,Default,,0,0,0,,If you eliminate it within the first second
Dialogue: 0,1:15:41.63,1:15:43.63,Default,,0,0,0,,it's 150 watts and it's 600 watts
Dialogue: 0,1:15:43.63,1:15:45.63,Default,,0,0,0,,then it's a have to.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:45.63,1:15:51.47,Default,,0,0,0,,You can interrupt
Dialogue: 0,1:15:51.47,1:15:53.47,Default,,0,0,0,,the progression by interrupting
Dialogue: 0,1:15:53.47,1:15:55.85,Default,,0,0,0,,the image.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:55.85,1:15:58.64,Default,,0,0,0,,So even if you look at something
Dialogue: 0,1:15:58.64,1:16:00.64,Default,,0,0,0,,a cheeseburger or whatever
Dialogue: 0,1:16:00.64,1:16:02.64,Default,,0,0,0,,it isn't just the cheeseburger
Dialogue: 0,1:16:02.64,1:16:04.64,Default,,0,0,0,,it's instantly now you have an image of the cheeseburger
Dialogue: 0,1:16:04.64,1:16:06.64,Default,,0,0,0,,in your mind and that's what you crave.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:06.64,1:16:11.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Therefore you have to be very fast
Dialogue: 0,1:16:11.68,1:16:14.19,Default,,0,0,0,,and see
Dialogue: 0,1:16:14.19,1:16:16.19,Default,,0,0,0,,the object of the cravingness
Dialogue: 0,1:16:16.19,1:16:18.19,Default,,0,0,0,,appear in your consciousness
Dialogue: 0,1:16:18.19,1:16:20.19,Default,,0,0,0,,and make a choice to eliminate it now.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:20.19,1:16:25.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah?
Dialogue: 0,1:16:25.11,1:16:27.21,Default,,0,0,0,,That's how you do it.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:27.21,1:16:29.21,Default,,0,0,0,,I was telling alcoholics
Dialogue: 0,1:16:29.21,1:16:31.21,Default,,0,0,0,,you've got about one or two seconds
Dialogue: 0,1:16:31.21,1:16:33.68,Default,,0,0,0,,to eliminate that image of a drink.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:33.68,1:16:35.68,Default,,0,0,0,,In the book Alcoholics Anonymous
Dialogue: 0,1:16:35.68,1:16:37.68,Default,,0,0,0,,it talks about some guy who was sober
Dialogue: 0,1:16:37.68,1:16:39.68,Default,,0,0,0,,14 years or something, 11 years
Dialogue: 0,1:16:39.68,1:16:41.94,Default,,0,0,0,,and he walked across
Dialogue: 0,1:16:41.94,1:16:43.94,Default,,0,0,0,,in the hall or something of a hotel
Dialogue: 0,1:16:43.94,1:16:45.94,Default,,0,0,0,,and the image of a martini
Dialogue: 0,1:16:45.94,1:16:47.94,Default,,0,0,0,,came into his mind
Dialogue: 0,1:16:47.94,1:16:49.94,Default,,0,0,0,,and mindlessly he walked to the bar
Dialogue: 0,1:16:49.94,1:16:51.94,Default,,0,0,0,,and after 13, 14 years
Dialogue: 0,1:16:51.94,1:16:54.03,Default,,0,0,0,,of sobriety
Dialogue: 0,1:16:54.03,1:16:56.30,Default,,0,0,0,,relapsed and got drunk.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:56.30,1:16:58.30,Default,,0,0,0,,So it was in that one second.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:58.30,1:17:00.30,Default,,0,0,0,,So you'll see that in the AA book
Dialogue: 0,1:17:00.30,1:17:03.73,Default,,0,0,0,,in which
Dialogue: 0,1:17:03.73,1:17:05.73,Default,,0,0,0,,the early members recount their experiences
Dialogue: 0,1:17:05.73,1:17:08.67,Default,,0,0,0,,that out of nowhere
Dialogue: 0,1:17:08.67,1:17:10.67,Default,,0,0,0,,suddenly appeared
Dialogue: 0,1:17:10.67,1:17:12.67,Default,,0,0,0,,the image of the martini.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:12.67,1:17:14.67,Default,,0,0,0,,That's when he had his chance.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:14.67,1:17:16.67,Default,,0,0,0,,When he didn't eliminate the martini
Dialogue: 0,1:17:16.67,1:17:18.67,Default,,0,0,0,,that instant he automatically
Dialogue: 0,1:17:18.67,1:17:20.67,Default,,0,0,0,,walked over to the bar
Dialogue: 0,1:17:20.67,1:17:23.56,Default,,0,0,0,,and lost 14 years of sobriety.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:23.56,1:17:25.56,Default,,0,0,0,,He didn't like consciously choose
Dialogue: 0,1:17:25.56,1:17:28.90,Default,,0,0,0,,he just didn't have the
Dialogue: 0,1:17:28.90,1:17:30.90,Default,,0,0,0,,consciousness technique
Dialogue: 0,1:17:30.90,1:17:37.15,Default,,0,0,0,,the spiritual technique.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:37.15,1:17:39.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Right? That's a secret.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:39.71,1:17:46.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't tell anybody.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:46.51,1:17:48.51,Default,,0,0,0,,A short question on the technique of surrender
Dialogue: 0,1:17:48.51,1:17:50.51,Default,,0,0,0,,as you described it
Dialogue: 0,1:17:50.51,1:17:52.51,Default,,0,0,0,,like in the final run
Dialogue: 0,1:17:52.51,1:17:54.51,Default,,0,0,0,,and like maybe more like
Dialogue: 0,1:17:54.51,1:17:56.51,Default,,0,0,0,,a confirmation maybe
Dialogue: 0,1:17:56.51,1:17:58.51,Default,,0,0,0,,when the sword is there
Dialogue: 0,1:17:58.51,1:18:00.51,Default,,0,0,0,,every sword has a hook
Dialogue: 0,1:18:00.51,1:18:02.64,Default,,0,0,0,,or a choose
Dialogue: 0,1:18:02.64,1:18:04.64,Default,,0,0,0,,and what I'm doing is
Dialogue: 0,1:18:04.64,1:18:06.64,Default,,0,0,0,,try to intuit the choose
Dialogue: 0,1:18:06.64,1:18:08.64,Default,,0,0,0,,so then the thought process
Dialogue: 0,1:18:08.64,1:18:10.64,Default,,0,0,0,,falls away?
Dialogue: 0,1:18:10.64,1:18:12.76,Default,,0,0,0,,I see you're trying to
Dialogue: 0,1:18:12.76,1:18:14.76,Default,,0,0,0,,eliminate thought before it reaches
Dialogue: 0,1:18:14.76,1:18:16.76,Default,,0,0,0,,the formation of the thought.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:16.76,1:18:19.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Eventually, yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:19.02,1:18:21.02,Default,,0,0,0,,You can feel the image
Dialogue: 0,1:18:21.02,1:18:23.02,Default,,0,0,0,,of a dogginess coming up
Dialogue: 0,1:18:23.02,1:18:25.02,Default,,0,0,0,,out of the nothingness
Dialogue: 0,1:18:25.02,1:18:27.02,Default,,0,0,0,,arises a dogginess
Dialogue: 0,1:18:27.02,1:18:29.02,Default,,0,0,0,,big dogginess and then it becomes
Dialogue: 0,1:18:29.02,1:18:31.02,Default,,0,0,0,,a dog, then it becomes an old rover
Dialogue: 0,1:18:31.02,1:18:33.02,Default,,0,0,0,,then it becomes how an old rover got hit by the car
Dialogue: 0,1:18:33.02,1:18:35.02,Default,,0,0,0,,and then how we all cried
Dialogue: 0,1:18:35.02,1:18:37.23,Default,,0,0,0,,and it was my daughter's third birthday
Dialogue: 0,1:18:37.23,1:18:39.23,Default,,0,0,0,,and the whole family was sad
Dialogue: 0,1:18:39.23,1:18:41.50,Default,,0,0,0,,I mean it's a whole long tale
Dialogue: 0,1:18:41.50,1:18:43.50,Default,,0,0,0,,so you have to catch it as it emerges.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:43.50,1:18:45.50,Default,,0,0,0,,And the way
Dialogue: 0,1:18:45.50,1:18:47.50,Default,,0,0,0,,to give up the choose
Dialogue: 0,1:18:47.50,1:18:49.52,Default,,0,0,0,,would be the best way to do it?
Dialogue: 0,1:18:49.52,1:18:51.52,Default,,0,0,0,,To give up wanting to have it?
Dialogue: 0,1:18:51.52,1:18:54.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Give up the image
Dialogue: 0,1:18:54.52,1:18:59.27,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't really tell you
Dialogue: 0,1:18:59.27,1:19:01.27,Default,,0,0,0,,how to do that. You have to
Dialogue: 0,1:19:01.27,1:19:03.27,Default,,0,0,0,,experiment with it and reflect on it.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:03.27,1:19:05.76,Default,,0,0,0,,You don't
Dialogue: 0,1:19:05.76,1:19:07.76,Default,,0,0,0,,allow, you feel the energy
Dialogue: 0,1:19:07.76,1:19:09.76,Default,,0,0,0,,of thinkingness begin to arise
Dialogue: 0,1:19:09.76,1:19:11.76,Default,,0,0,0,,and now it's going to spill forth
Dialogue: 0,1:19:11.76,1:19:13.85,Default,,0,0,0,,figure.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:13.85,1:19:15.85,Default,,0,0,0,,So you let go the energy
Dialogue: 0,1:19:15.85,1:19:17.85,Default,,0,0,0,,of wanting to think
Dialogue: 0,1:19:17.85,1:19:19.85,Default,,0,0,0,,earlier and earlier
Dialogue: 0,1:19:19.85,1:19:21.85,Default,,0,0,0,,in the process.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:21.85,1:19:23.85,Default,,0,0,0,,It feels like a desire?
Dialogue: 0,1:19:23.85,1:19:26.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes it is, that's correct.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:26.30,1:19:30.60,Default,,0,0,0,,A desire to think.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:30.60,1:19:32.60,Default,,0,0,0,,You're going to feel like an attack
Dialogue: 0,1:19:32.60,1:19:34.60,Default,,0,0,0,,of thinkingness is coming on you.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:34.60,1:19:39.96,Default,,0,0,0,,When it's that much thinking
Dialogue: 0,1:19:39.96,1:19:42.38,Default,,0,0,0,,don't meditate, do something else
Dialogue: 0,1:19:42.38,1:19:44.67,Default,,0,0,0,,until it's gone.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:44.67,1:19:46.67,Default,,0,0,0,,That's very good.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:46.67,1:19:48.67,Default,,0,0,0,,It comes out of no form
Dialogue: 0,1:19:48.67,1:19:50.67,Default,,0,0,0,,it begins to gather form
Dialogue: 0,1:19:50.67,1:19:52.72,Default,,0,0,0,,and as it gathers form it gathers energy.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:52.72,1:19:54.72,Default,,0,0,0,,And by the time it gets to over over
Dialogue: 0,1:19:54.72,1:19:56.72,Default,,0,0,0,,and now you've got to run over by the truck
Dialogue: 0,1:19:56.72,1:20:00.48,Default,,0,0,0,,it's too late already.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:00.48,1:20:06.07,Default,,0,0,0,,You stay on the advancing edge
Dialogue: 0,1:20:06.07,1:20:08.07,Default,,0,0,0,,just prior to thinkingness.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:08.07,1:20:12.76,Default,,0,0,0,,And you see your thinkingness
Dialogue: 0,1:20:12.76,1:20:21.22,Default,,0,0,0,,as just amusement anyway.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:21.22,1:20:23.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Dr. Hawkins,
Dialogue: 0,1:20:23.22,1:20:25.22,Default,,0,0,0,,recently I've been shown to be aware
Dialogue: 0,1:20:25.22,1:20:27.22,Default,,0,0,0,,of my
Dialogue: 0,1:20:27.22,1:20:29.22,Default,,0,0,0,,self-centeredness.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:29.22,1:20:31.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait a minute.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:31.22,1:20:33.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Get closer to the mic and speak slowly.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:33.22,1:20:35.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Recently I've been made to be aware
Dialogue: 0,1:20:35.22,1:20:37.22,Default,,0,0,0,,of self-centeredness.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:37.22,1:20:39.22,Default,,0,0,0,,My self-centeredness?
Dialogue: 0,1:20:39.22,1:20:41.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Self-centeredness.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:41.22,1:20:43.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh yes.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:43.28,1:20:45.28,Default,,0,0,0,,And I want to ask you how to work on that.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:45.28,1:20:47.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Well it's like self-centeredness
Dialogue: 0,1:20:47.28,1:20:49.57,Default,,0,0,0,,is watching yourself in the movie.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:49.57,1:20:51.57,Default,,0,0,0,,So give up watching yourself in the movie.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:51.57,1:20:57.60,Default,,0,0,0,,See they're signing the book, right?
Dialogue: 0,1:20:57.60,1:20:59.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Then I could also be
Dialogue: 0,1:20:59.77,1:21:01.77,Default,,0,0,0,,aware of who's signing the book
Dialogue: 0,1:21:01.77,1:21:03.77,Default,,0,0,0,,and the fact that you're signing a book.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:03.77,1:21:07.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Look at all that, it's boring.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:07.43,1:21:12.18,Default,,0,0,0,,It's boring.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:12.18,1:21:14.18,Default,,0,0,0,,That's how self-centeredness can be.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:14.18,1:21:16.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Now I'm sitting in the chair
Dialogue: 0,1:21:16.18,1:21:18.18,Default,,0,0,0,,and I'm talking to Dr. Hawkins
Dialogue: 0,1:21:18.18,1:21:20.43,Default,,0,0,0,,and you see how boring all that is?
Dialogue: 0,1:21:20.43,1:21:22.43,Default,,0,0,0,,So that's a self,
Dialogue: 0,1:21:22.43,1:21:24.92,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know,
Dialogue: 0,1:21:24.92,1:21:26.92,Default,,0,0,0,,sort of like you're doing a video
Dialogue: 0,1:21:26.92,1:21:29.11,Default,,0,0,0,,of yourself at the same time.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:29.11,1:21:31.11,Default,,0,0,0,,You see what I mean?
Dialogue: 0,1:21:31.11,1:21:33.11,Default,,0,0,0,,And it's a habit of thought.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:33.11,1:21:35.11,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a habit of thought.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:35.11,1:21:37.11,Default,,0,0,0,,And once you're aware that you're doing it
Dialogue: 0,1:21:37.11,1:21:39.78,Default,,0,0,0,,as a habit, it tends to diminish.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:39.78,1:21:41.78,Default,,0,0,0,,You just do what you're doing
Dialogue: 0,1:21:41.78,1:21:44.23,Default,,0,0,0,,without being aware that there's a you
Dialogue: 0,1:21:44.23,1:21:48.00,Default,,0,0,0,,see?
Dialogue: 0,1:21:54.18,1:21:56.18,Default,,0,0,0,,That happens of its own.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:56.18,1:21:58.18,Default,,0,0,0,,You don't say, well Dr. Hawkins,
Dialogue: 0,1:21:58.18,1:22:00.18,Default,,0,0,0,,I think while I'm talking to her
Dialogue: 0,1:22:00.18,1:22:02.18,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll wave my hands in the air
Dialogue: 0,1:22:02.18,1:22:04.18,Default,,0,0,0,,and go blah blah blah blah blah.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:04.18,1:22:06.31,Default,,0,0,0,,You know how boring that would be?
Dialogue: 0,1:22:06.31,1:22:08.31,Default,,0,0,0,,It would kill the spontaneity of it.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:08.31,1:22:10.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Intuitively you try to respond
Dialogue: 0,1:22:10.31,1:22:12.31,Default,,0,0,0,,in a nonverbal manner because
Dialogue: 0,1:22:12.31,1:22:15.76,Default,,0,0,0,,otherwise people mentalize
Dialogue: 0,1:22:15.76,1:22:17.76,Default,,0,0,0,,a mentalization.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:17.76,1:22:19.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Spontaneously just be that which you are
Dialogue: 0,1:22:19.76,1:22:22.39,Default,,0,0,0,,without any comment, without any witnessing of it.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:22.39,1:22:24.68,Default,,0,0,0,,They say when you scramble eggs
Dialogue: 0,1:22:24.68,1:22:26.68,Default,,0,0,0,,don't be saying, gee how good am I
Dialogue: 0,1:22:26.68,1:22:28.68,Default,,0,0,0,,scrambling these eggs.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:28.68,1:22:30.90,Default,,0,0,0,,That ruins the eggs for one thing.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:30.90,1:22:38.92,Default,,0,0,0,,It's like one's higher self
Dialogue: 0,1:22:38.92,1:22:40.92,Default,,0,0,0,,knows all these things
Dialogue: 0,1:22:40.92,1:22:42.92,Default,,0,0,0,,and you don't have to track it
Dialogue: 0,1:22:42.92,1:22:50.30,Default,,0,0,0,,with your lower self.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:50.30,1:22:52.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Just noticing it tends to diminish it.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:52.30,1:22:54.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Just noticing it.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:54.30,1:22:56.77,Default,,0,0,0,,See?
Dialogue: 0,1:22:56.77,1:22:58.77,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't say, now I am sitting in a chair
Dialogue: 0,1:22:58.77,1:23:00.77,Default,,0,0,0,,on a pillow and talking to you.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:00.77,1:23:03.13,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't say that, right?
Dialogue: 0,1:23:03.13,1:23:05.13,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sort of saying, now I'm sitting in a chair
Dialogue: 0,1:23:05.13,1:23:07.13,Default,,0,0,0,,talking to you.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:07.13,1:23:09.13,Default,,0,0,0,,So what I want you to do is get bored with
Dialogue: 0,1:23:09.13,1:23:12.06,Default,,0,0,0,,self observation.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:12.06,1:23:14.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Mindfulness is something else.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:14.06,1:23:16.06,Default,,0,0,0,,We're talking about now self observation.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:16.06,1:23:18.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Mindfulness will tell you that
Dialogue: 0,1:23:18.06,1:23:20.06,Default,,0,0,0,,you're hooked in self observation.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:20.06,1:23:22.06,Default,,0,0,0,,That's what you're complaining about.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:22.06,1:23:24.06,Default,,0,0,0,,But that came out of mindfulness
Dialogue: 0,1:23:24.06,1:23:26.06,Default,,0,0,0,,which is something better.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:26.06,1:23:28.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Mindfulness is okay.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:28.82,1:23:32.77,Default,,0,0,0,,You have mindfulness
Dialogue: 0,1:23:32.77,1:23:34.77,Default,,0,0,0,,that's why you're complaining about it.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:34.77,1:23:38.92,Default,,0,0,0,,If you weren't mindful you wouldn't know
Dialogue: 0,1:23:38.92,1:23:40.92,Default,,0,0,0,,and you just think that's the way I am.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:40.92,1:23:44.27,Default,,0,0,0,,So that means good progress.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:44.27,1:24:05.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Where do these come from?
Dialogue: 0,1:24:05.65,1:24:07.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Hi. Hello.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:07.94,1:24:09.94,Default,,0,0,0,,I've simplified this question as much as I can
Dialogue: 0,1:24:09.94,1:24:11.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Dr. Hawkins.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:11.94,1:24:13.94,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't seem to have enough physical energy
Dialogue: 0,1:24:13.94,1:24:15.94,Default,,0,0,0,,to do what I want to do right now.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:15.94,1:24:18.23,Default,,0,0,0,,And I want to know
Dialogue: 0,1:24:18.23,1:24:20.23,Default,,0,0,0,,what the obstacle is blocking
Dialogue: 0,1:24:20.23,1:24:22.97,Default,,0,0,0,,my physical energy.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:25.68,1:24:27.68,Default,,0,0,0,,The intention may not be as strong as you
Dialogue: 0,1:24:27.68,1:24:29.68,Default,,0,0,0,,I mean
Dialogue: 0,1:24:29.68,1:24:31.68,Default,,0,0,0,,if you're into ought to, ought to
Dialogue: 0,1:24:31.68,1:24:33.89,Default,,0,0,0,,this and ought to that.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:33.89,1:24:35.89,Default,,0,0,0,,That's the hypothetical.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:35.89,1:24:37.89,Default,,0,0,0,,How do you know the ought to has any
Dialogue: 0,1:24:37.89,1:24:42.17,Default,,0,0,0,,reality to it?
Dialogue: 0,1:24:42.17,1:24:44.17,Default,,0,0,0,,I ought to be peeling more potatoes than I am.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:44.17,1:24:46.17,Default,,0,0,0,,I ought to be able to peel eight
Dialogue: 0,1:24:46.17,1:24:48.72,Default,,0,0,0,,and I only peel four.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:48.72,1:24:50.72,Default,,0,0,0,,That's projecting the hypothetical.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:50.72,1:24:52.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Why not just settle for the real?
Dialogue: 0,1:24:52.72,1:24:54.72,Default,,0,0,0,,You can only peel four potatoes at this time
Dialogue: 0,1:24:54.72,1:24:56.77,Default,,0,0,0,,in your life.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:56.77,1:24:59.19,Default,,0,0,0,,And don't invite a lot of company for dinner.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:59.19,1:25:04.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Can I do a follow up?
Dialogue: 0,1:25:04.81,1:25:06.81,Default,,0,0,0,,I mean
Dialogue: 0,1:25:06.81,1:25:08.81,Default,,0,0,0,,I think along the spiritual pathway there's
Dialogue: 0,1:25:08.81,1:25:10.88,Default,,0,0,0,,periods, sometimes long periods
Dialogue: 0,1:25:10.88,1:25:12.88,Default,,0,0,0,,where your capacity to function is really curtailed.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:12.88,1:25:15.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Really curtailed.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:15.71,1:25:19.21,Default,,0,0,0,,You say
Dialogue: 0,1:25:19.21,1:25:21.21,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't think I have the energy to
Dialogue: 0,1:25:21.21,1:25:23.56,Default,,0,0,0,,put my shoes and socks
Dialogue: 0,1:25:23.56,1:25:26.90,Default,,0,0,0,,on today.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:26.90,1:25:28.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Somehow the instinct of survival
Dialogue: 0,1:25:28.90,1:25:30.90,Default,,0,0,0,,takes over and you do what you need
Dialogue: 0,1:25:30.90,1:25:34.11,Default,,0,0,0,,to do.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:34.11,1:25:36.11,Default,,0,0,0,,So I wouldn't worry about it.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:36.11,1:25:38.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Between expectation and
Dialogue: 0,1:25:38.11,1:25:40.69,Default,,0,0,0,,actual capacity.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:40.69,1:25:42.69,Default,,0,0,0,,In spiritual endeavor a great deal of energy
Dialogue: 0,1:25:42.69,1:25:44.69,Default,,0,0,0,,goes into the spiritual work
Dialogue: 0,1:25:44.69,1:25:47.11,Default,,0,0,0,,and you don't realize it.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:47.11,1:25:49.36,Default,,0,0,0,,But
Dialogue: 0,1:25:49.36,1:25:51.36,Default,,0,0,0,,it siphons off a lot of energy
Dialogue: 0,1:25:51.36,1:25:53.36,Default,,0,0,0,,that would otherwise go into physicality
Dialogue: 0,1:25:53.36,1:25:56.07,Default,,0,0,0,,and movement, etc.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:56.07,1:26:02.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:02.75,1:26:04.75,Default,,0,0,0,,There are periods where you do nothing.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:04.75,1:26:06.75,Default,,0,0,0,,I spent several years just meditating
Dialogue: 0,1:26:06.75,1:26:11.18,Default,,0,0,0,,and doing nothing.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:11.18,1:26:13.88,Default,,0,0,0,,In the view of the world, doing nothing.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:13.88,1:26:17.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Sat cross-legged for years.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:17.52,1:26:19.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you very much.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:19.52,1:26:21.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Black widow spiders were underneath the
Dialogue: 0,1:26:21.52,1:26:23.57,Default,,0,0,0,,seat in fact.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:23.57,1:26:25.57,Default,,0,0,0,,One time I looked down there and
Dialogue: 0,1:26:25.57,1:26:27.57,Default,,0,0,0,,I was just sitting there meditating
Dialogue: 0,1:26:27.57,1:26:29.57,Default,,0,0,0,,in this place for years
Dialogue: 0,1:26:29.57,1:26:31.57,Default,,0,0,0,,and there were black widow spiders
Dialogue: 0,1:26:31.57,1:26:35.23,Default,,0,0,0,,living under the chair.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:35.23,1:26:38.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Evil spirits, huh?
Dialogue: 0,1:26:38.77,1:26:42.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
